niversary%20of%20Swami%20Vivekananda%20was%20celebrated%20on%20January%2012%20when%20there%20is%20massive%20publicity%20campaign%20launched%20by%20Narendra%20Modi%20regime%20for%20the%20consecration%20of%20Ram%20in%20Ayodhya%20on%20January%2022%2C%20exactly%20in%20the%20same%20site%20where%20on%20December%206%2C%201992%2C%20the%20Babri%20mosque%20was%20demolished%20and%20Supreme%20Court%20held%20that%20to%20be%20an%20egregious%20violation%20of%20rule%20law.%20There%20is%20massive%20controversy%20being%20generated%20by%20BJP%20around%20Congress%20leaders%20and%20others%20who%20declined%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20much%20hyped-consecration%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20Shankaracharya%20also%20declined%20to%20participate%20on%20several%20grounds%2C%20one%20of%20which%20is%20that%20the%20temple%20is%20not%20completely%20constructed%20and%20so%20it%20is%20in%20contravention%20of%20scriptural%20injunction%20not%20to%20consecrate%20the%20deity%20in%20an%20incomplete%20shrine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENote%20that%20Swami%20Vivekananda%20was%20not%20allowed%20to%20visit%20Odisha%20temples%20after%20his%20return%20to%20India%20following%20his%20triumphant%20visit%20to%20the%20USA%20in%201893%20to%20address%20several%20lectures%20including%20in%20the%20famous%20event%20organised%20by%20World%20Parliament%20of%20Religions%20in%20Chicago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20here%20is%20an%20example%20of%20cerebral%20monk%20of%20Hinduism%20who%20mesmerised%20Americans%20by%20his%20brilliant%20exposition%20of%20spirituality%20and%20Vedanta%20and%20yet%20was%20told%20that%20he%20would%20not%20be%20allowed%20entry%20to%20temples%20of%20Odisha.%20In%20Volume%205%20of%20Swami%20Vivekananda%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EComplete%20Works%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Eon%20page%20number%20171%2C%20there%20is%20a%20letter%20Swami%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20wrote%20to%20one%20Josephine%20MacLeod.%20In%20that%2C%20he%20wrote%20with%20anguish%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20do%20not%20know%20whether%20it%20will%20be%20possible%20to%20see%20the%20Orissan%20temples%20in%20company%20with%20your%20Japanese%20friends%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20do%20not%20know%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwhether%20I%20shall%20be%20allowed%20myself%20owing%20to%20my%20eating%20%E2%80%9CMlechchha%20Food%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Swami%20Vivekananda%20was%20dubbed%20as%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Emlechchha%3C%2Fem%3E%20food%E2%80%9D%20eater%20because%20he%20ate%20food%20cooked%20by%20Christians%20in%20America%20and%20was%20not%20allowed%20to%20enter%20those%20temples%20of%20Orissa%2C%20present%20day%20Odisha%2C%20now%20Congress%20leaders%20refusing%20to%20join%20the%20Ram%20temple%20event%20in%20Ayodhya%20are%20dubbed%20as%20Ram-%3Cem%3Edrohis%20%3C%2Fem%3Eor%20traitors%20to%20Ram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20illuminating%20to%20not%20that%20Swami%20Vivekananda%20also%20reflected%20on%20the%20establishment%20of%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20which%20was%20established%20in%201885%20by%20Allan%20Octavian%20Hume%2C%20a%20British%20national.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEleven%20years%20later%20in%201896%20while%20Vivekananda%20was%20in%20London%2C%20he%20was%20asked%20a%20question%3A%20%E2%80%9CHave%20you%20given%20any%20attention%20to%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20moment%3F%E2%80%9D%20In%20his%20response%20he%20said%20that%20he%20did%20not%20pay%20enough%20attention%20to%20it%20and%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6I%20regard%20the%20movement%20as%20significant%2C%20and%20heartily%20wish%20it%20success.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20further%2C%20he%20said%20that%20a%20nation%20was%20being%20made%20out%20of%20different%20races%20which%20in%20terms%20of%20variety%20remained%20no%20less%20plural%20than%20different%20peoples%20of%20Europe.%20He%20interpreted%20the%20acquisition%20of%20Indian%20trade%20by%20several%20European%20countries%20such%20as%20Britain%2C%20Dutch%2C%20Portugal%20and%20French%20as%20%E2%80%9Ca%20turning%20point%20in%20the%20history%20of%20humanity%E2%80%9D%20and%20described%20that%20the%20trade%20and%20commerce%20of%20India%20played%20%C2%A0a%20%C2%A0tremendous%20part%20in%20the%20civilisation%20of%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20in%20what%20direction%20it%20would%20proceed%20to%20attain%20finality%2C%20Vivekananda%20very%20presciently%2C%20said%20that%20it%20would%20lead%20to%2C%20in%20his%20words%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6the%20working%20out%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20homogeneity%2C%20in%20her%20acquiring%20what%20we%20may%20call%20democratic%20ideas.%E2%80%9D%20He%20went%20on%20to%20state%20that%20monopoly%20over%20intelligence%20and%20education%20by%20a%20cultured%20few%20should%20come%20to%20an%20end%2C%20provision%20of%20education%20should%20be%20accompanied%20with%20compulsory%20education%20and%20immense%20power%20of%20people%20should%20be%20utilised%20to%20actualise%20India%E2%80%99s%20potential.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Vivekananda%20was%20asked%20if%20India%20was%20sensitive%20and%20conscious%20of%20%C2%A0the%20awakening%20that%20he%20alluded%20to%2C%20his%20response%20was%3A%20%E2%80%9CPerfectly%20conscious%2C%20The%20world%20perhaps%20sees%20it%20chiefly%20in%20the%20Congress%20movement%20and%20in%20the%20field%20of%20social%20reform.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201898%20when%20someone%20told%20Swami%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20%C2%A0that%20India%20National%20Congress%20and%20other%20patriotic%20organisations%20were%20carrying%20on%20strenuous%20agitation%20and%20petitioning%20the%20British%20government%2C%20he%20remarked%20that%20the%20rulers%E2%80%99%20duty%20was%20to%20address%20the%20problems%20of%20the%20people.%20In%20that%20context%20he%20flagged%20the%20point%20as%20to%20who%20would%20continue%20to%20place%20people%E2%80%99s%20%C2%A0issues%20before%20the%20government.%20He%20asked%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhere%20are%20the%20men%20who%20are%20the%20able%20to%20keep%20up%20things%20demanded%3F%E2%80%9D%20and%20suggested%2C%20%E2%80%9CSo%20make%20men%20first%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%20it%20was%20that%20Swami%20Vivekananda%20spoke%20thus%20of%20just%2013%20years%20after%20the%20establishment%20of%20Congress%20in%201885.%20This%20organisation%20is%20now%20criticised%20by%20none%20other%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fafternoon-brief-congress-founded-by-foreigner-pm-modis-jibe-and-all-the-latest-news-101690268315900.html%5C%22%3Ethan%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20for%20having%20been%20set%20up%20by%20a%20foreigner.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVivekananda%E2%80%99s%20ideas%20in%20the%20context%20of%20agitations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESwami%20Vivekananda%E2%80%99s%20words%20%E2%80%9CWhere%20are%20the%20men%20who%20are%20able%20to%20keep%20up%20things%20demanded%E2%80%9D%20resonate%20in%20the%20several%20movements%20of%20people%20including%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20and%20now%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%2C%20being%20launched%20on%20January%2014.%20His%20vision%20is%20being%20%C2%A0carried%20%C2%A0forward%20by%20people%20engaged%20in%20several%20agitations%20with%20the%20ability%20to%20%E2%80%9Ckeep%20up%20things%20demanded.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20why%20Swami%20Vivekananda%20was%20often%20invoking%20the%20stirring%20words%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3EUpanishad%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%9CArise%2C%20awake%20and%20stop%20not%20till%20the%20goal%20is%20reached%E2%80%9D.%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20as%20prime%20minister%20of%20India%20had%20started%20celebrating%20Swami%20Vivekananda%E2%80%99s%20birthday%20as%20National%20Youth%20Day.%20Days%20after%20his%20birth%20anniversary%2C%20India%20must%20remain%20tuned%20to%20his%20words%20uttered%20in%20Chicago%20%E2%80%93%20that%20%E2%80%9Csectarianism%2C%20bigotry%20and%20its%20horrible%20descendent%20fanaticism%20drenched%20the%20earth%20with%20the%20blood%20of%20innocents%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20hope%20that%20the%20bell%20that%20tolled%20to%20announce%20the%20commencement%20of%20the%20World%20Parliament%20of%20Religions%20would%20be%20the%20death%20knell%20of%20fanaticism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0S.N.%20Sahu%20served%20as%20Officer%20on%20Special%20Duty%20to%20President%20of%20India%20K.R.%20Narayanan.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705288347000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F15081307%2FScreenshot-2024-01-14-at-7.23.47.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fa-lesson-on-temples-from-swami-vivekananda%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Swami%20Vivekananda%20was%20not%20allowed%20to%20visit%20Odisha%20temples%20after%20his%20return%20to%20India%20following%20his%20triumphant%20visit%20to%20the%20USA%20in%201893%20to%20address%20several%20lectures%20including%20in%20the%20famous%20event%20organised%20by%20World%20Parliament%20of%20Religions%20in%20Chicago.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fa-lesson-on-temples-from-swami-vivekananda%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20'True%20Detective'%20season%204%20opens%20on%20a%20subtle%20season%201%20Easter%20egg%20and%20a%20Billie%20Eilish%20song%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jodie%20Foster%20wearing%20glasses%20on%20%26quot%3BTrue%20Detective%3A%20Night%20Country.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a064256979d7371822ab51%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJodie%20Foster%20on%20%26quot%3BTrue%20Detective%3A%20Night%20Country.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EMichele%20K.%20Short%2FHBO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWarning%3A%20There%20are%20minor%20spoilers%20ahead%20for%20%26quot%3BTrue%20Detective%3A%20Night%20Country.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20quote%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20season%20refers%20to%20%26quot%3BThe%20King%20In%20Yellow%2C%26quot%3B%20referenced%20in%20the%20show's%20first%20season.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShowrunner%C2%A0Issa%20L%C3%B3pez%20created%20the%20fake%20quote%20as%20a%20nod%20to%20season%20one.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESeason%20four%20of%20%26quot%3BTrue%20Detective%26quot%3B%20kicked%20off%20Sunday%20night%20with%20an%20ominous%20quote%20that%20has%20deep%20ties%20to%20the%20show's%20lore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%26quot%3BFor%20we%20do%20not%20know%20what%20beasts%20the%20night%20dreams%20when%20its%20hours%20grow%20too%20long%20for%20even%20God%20to%20be%20awake%2C%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20Hildred%20Castaigne%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20a%20big%20%26quot%3BTrue%20Detective%26quot%3B%20fan%2C%20you%20may%20recognize%20Castaigne%20as%20a%20fictional%20character%20appearing%20in%20Robert%20W.%20Chambers'%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Dd51ae099bf1b7771bfb91cb1d9ce0b28a35057c8d830c24da7d87e85ceafd9b7%26postID%3D65a02fa2d137673d8c98bfb4%26postSlug%3Dtrue-detective-season-4-premiere-quote-season-1-connection-billie-eilish-2024-1%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FKing-Yellow-Robert-W-Chambers%252Fdp%252F0809557541%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20King%20in%20Yellow.%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%201895%20collection%20of%20short%20stories%20is%20referenced%20throughout%20the%20show's%20first%20season%20in%20a%20journal%20and%20through%20mention%20of%20The%20Yellow%20King%2C%20an%20evil%20entity%20who%20was%20worshipped%20and%20connected%20to%20a%20series%20of%20murders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Top%20image%20shows%20Woody%20Harrelson%20looks%20at%20Matthew%20McConaughey%20as%20he%20reads%20from%20a%20journal%20on%20season%20one%20of%20%26quot%3BTrue%20Detective.%26quot%3B%20The%20bottom%20image%20shows%20a%20peek%20at%20the%20journal%20which%20contains%20drawings%20and%20scribblings%20of%20words%20including%20%26quot%3BThe%20Yellow%20King.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a063436979d7371822aaf6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221330%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOn%20season%20one%2C%20episode%20two%20of%20%26quot%3BTrue%20Detective%26quot%3B%20Matthew%20McConaughey's%20character%2C%20Rust%2C%20reads%20from%20the%20diary%20of%20a%20murdered%20woman%20and%20spies%20the%20words%20%26quot%3BThe%20Yellow%20King%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BCarcosa%26quot%3B%20in%20it.%3Cp%3EHBO%3B%20composite%20by%20Kirsten%20Acuna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20you%20try%20and%20search%20for%20the%20quote%2C%20you%20won't%20find%20it%20in%20Chambers'%20work.%20That's%20because%20it's%20made%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20a%20quote%20%5Bfrom%5D%20myself%2C%26quot%3B%20showrunner%20Issa%20L%C3%B3pez%20told%20Business%20Insider%20last%20month%20over%20Zoom.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20looking%20for%20the%20perfect%20quote%20to%20talk%20about%20the%20things%20that%20hide%20in%20the%20dark%20and%20I%20couldn't%20find%20it.%20So%20I%20wrote%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAttributing%20the%20fake%20quote%20to%20Castaigne%20was%20a%20fun%20way%20to%20work%20in%20%26quot%3Ba%20little%20wink%26quot%3B%20to%20season%20one%20for%20the%20fans%2C%20said%20L%C3%B3pez.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20particularly%20a%20fan%20of%20the%20supernatural%20vein%20in%20the%20first%20season%2C%20The%20Yellow%20King%20and%20Carcosa%2C%26quot%3B%20L%C3%B3pez%20said%2C%20referencing%20the%20temple%20dedicated%20to%20the%20mysterious%20being%20on%20season%20one.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20read%20those%20books%20years%20ago%2C%20but%20I%20went%20back%20again%20and%20I%20went%2C%20'Who%20could%20be%20the%20writer%20of%20these%20quotes%3F'%20And%20I%20created%20the%20idea%20that%20it%20was%20Hildred%20Castaigne%20who%20wrote%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTrue%20Detective%3A%20Night%20Country%26quot%3B%20follows%20Detectives%20Liz%20Danvers%20(Jodie%20Foster)%20and%20Evangeline%20Navarro%20(Kali%20Reis)%20as%20they%20investigate%20the%20mysterious%20disappearance%20of%20eight%20researchers%20in%20Alaska%20as%20they%20experience%20the%20final%20sunset%20of%20the%20year%20in%20mid-December.%20The%20pair%20are%20led%20on%20a%20supernatural%20journey%20that%20has%20them%20chasing%20leads%20and%20reconciling%20with%20their%20own%20deep-seated%20traumas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20opening%20quote%20and%20the%20idea%20of%20unrelenting%20darkness%20will%20have%20resonance%20throughout%20the%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThings%20happen%20when%20the%20dark%20goes%20for%20too%20long%2C%26quot%3B%20L%C3%B3pez%20said.%20%26quot%3BThings%20crawl%20out%20of%20the%20corners%20that%20shy%20from%20the%20light%2C%20and%20if%20you%20keep%20it%20dark%20long%20enough%2C%20secrets%20are%20going%20to%20come%20to%20the%20surface.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20L%C3%B3pez%20landed%20on%20a%20Billie%20Eilish%20hit%20for%20the%20'True%20Detective'%20season%204%20opening%20credits%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kali%20Reis%20and%20Jodie%20Foster%20on%20%26quot%3BTrue%20Detective%3A%20Night%20Country.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a0653a43bb77284b9c7cb1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221283%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKali%20Reis%20and%20Jodie%20Foster%20on%20%26quot%3BTrue%20Detective%3A%20Night%20Country.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EMichele%20K.%20Short%2FHBO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPaired%20with%20the%20season's%20otherworldly%20vibe%20is%20Billie%20Eilish's%20%26quot%3BBury%20a%20Friend%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20serves%20as%20the%20show's%20theme%20song%20over%20an%20elaborate%20title%20sequence.%20L%C3%B3pez%20said%20it%20was%20a%20natural%20fit%2C%20as%20she%20wrote%20the%20series%20listening%20to%20songs%20from%20the%20Grammy%20winner%20and%20Eilish's%20collaborator%20and%20brother%2C%20Finneas%20O'Connell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20knew%20that%20the%20series%20was%20going%20to%20need%20a%20powerful%20anthem%2C%20a%20showstopper%2C%20honestly%2C%26quot%3B%20L%C3%B3pez%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20were%20doing%20the%20titles%2C%20I%20tried%20several%20things%20and%20then%20I%20realized%20that%20the%20lyrics%20of%20this%20song%20seem%20to%20be%20written%20for%20the%20series%2C%26quot%3B%20L%C3%B3pez%20said%20of%20Eilish's%202019%20song%20about%20a%20monster%20under%20someone's%20bed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20crazy.%20It%20talks%20about%20a%20tongue%2C%20about%20burying%20your%20friend.%20It%20seemed%20that%20it%20was%20made%20for%20the%20show%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20continued.%20%26quot%3BSo%20we%20tried%20it%20and%20it%20just%20matched%20and%20it%20was%20meant%20to%20be.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20'True%20Detective%3A%20Night%20Country'%20opening%20credits%20are%20filled%20with%20clues%20about%20the%20season%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Issa%20L%C3%B3pez%20and%20Jodie%20Foster%20behind-the-scenes%20of%20%26quot%3BTrue%20Detective%3A%20Night%20Country.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a066d06979d7371822acaa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIssa%20L%C3%B3pez%20and%20Jodie%20Foster%20behind-the-scenes%20of%20%26quot%3BTrue%20Detective%3A%20Night%20Country.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EMichele%20K.%20Short%20%2F%20HBO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20Eilish's%20song%20that%20makes%20the%20credits%20noteworthy.%20L%C3%B3pez%20told%20BI%20that%20viewers%20should%20keep%20a%20closer%20eye%20on%20the%20imagery%20in%20the%20show's%20opening%20sequence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20clues%20in%20those%20titles%2C%26quot%3B%20L%C3%B3pez%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20were%20made%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.peterandersonstudio.co.uk%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPeter%20Anderson%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who's%20an%20absolute%20genius.%20He%20did%20'Good%20Omens'%20and%20'Bad%20Sisters.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20imagery%2C%20including%20a%20polar%20bear%20and%20a%20peeled%20orange%2C%20contains%20hints%20about%20what's%20to%20come%20to%20keep%20fans%20guessing%20all%20season.%20The%20title%20sequence's%20last%20shot%2C%20which%20changes%20week%20to%20week%2C%20teases%20an%20upcoming%20moment%20in%20that%20week's%20episode.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20both%20went%20crazy%20with%20this%2C%20thinking%20of%20all%20the%20little%20clues%20that%20we%20could%20put%20in%20the%20show%2C%26quot%3B%20L%C3%B3pez%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BTrue%20Detective%3A%20Night%20Country%26quot%3B%20airs%20Sunday%20nights%20at%209%20p.m.%20on%20HBO.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrue-detective-season-4-premiere-quote-season-1-connection-billie-eilish-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705287662000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a065b66979d7371822ac09%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrue-detective-season-4-premiere-quote-season-1-connection-billie-eilish-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BTrue%20Detective%26quot%3B%20showrunner%20Issa%20L%C3%B3pez%20explains%20why%20the%20new%20season%2C%20titled%20%26quot%3BNight%20Country%2C%26quot%3B%20opens%20on%20a%20fake%20quote%20that%20references%20season%201.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kacuna%40businessinsider.com%20(Kirsten%20Acuna)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrue-detective-season-4-premiere-quote-season-1-connection-billie-eilish-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98True%20Detective%3A%20Night%20Country%E2%80%99%20Premiere%20Analysis%3A%