d%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya.%20The%20Department%20of%20Telecommunications%20(DoT)%20is%20using%20AI%20and%20ML%20to%20ensure%20seamless%20connectivity%20for%20the%20millions%20expected%20to%20attend.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fai-steps-in-to-ensure-seamless-connectivity-for-ayodhya-ram-temple-inauguration%2Farticleshow%2F106847806.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Video%3A%20Passenger%20Hits%20IndiGo%20Pilot%20Announcing%20Flight%20Delay%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20passenger%20aboard%20an%20IndiGo%20flight%20physically%20assaulted%20the%20aircraft's%20pilot%20while%20he%20was%20making%20an%20announcement%20regarding%20delays.%20A%20video%20of%20the%20assault%20is%20now%20viral%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shocking%20episode%20unfolded%20as%20a%20man%20in%20a%20yellow%20hoodie%20abruptly%20ran%20up%20from%20the%20last%20row%20and%20hit%20the%20new%20pilot%2C%20who%20had%20replaced%20the%20previous%20crew%20due%20to%20Flight%20Duty%20Time%20Limitations%20(FDTL)%20norms%20after%20several%20hours%20of%20delay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EA%20passenger%20punched%20an%20Indigo%20capt%20in%20the%20aircraft%20as%20he%20was%20making%20delay%20announcement.%20The%20guy%20ran%20up%20from%20the%20last%20row%20and%20punched%20the%20new%20Capt%20who%20replaced%20the%20previous%20crew%20who%20crossed%20FDTL.%20Unbelievable%20!%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDGCAIndia%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40DGCAIndia%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMoCA_GoI%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40MoCA_GoI%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FSkdlpWbaDd%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FSkdlpWbaDd%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Capt_Ck%20(%40Capt_Ck)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCapt_Ck%2Fstatus%2F1746611192846807189%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2014%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFDTL%2C%20or%20Flight%20Duty%20Time%20Limitations%2C%20are%20regulations%20crucial%20for%20ensuring%20the%20well-being%20of%20pilots%20and%20flight%20attendants%20by%20mandating%20adequate%20rest%20periods%20and%20mitigating%20fatigue-related%20safety%20concerns.%20The%20responsibility%20for%20establishing%20FDTL%20falls%20under%20the%20jurisdiction%20of%20the%20Directorate-General%20of%20Civil%20Aviation%20(DGCA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20still%20unverified%20on%20which%20flight%20this%20incident%20took%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20does%20the%20pilot%20or%20cabin%20crew%20have%20to%20do%20with%20the%20delay%3F%20They%20were%20just%20doing%20their%20job.%20Arrest%20this%20man%2C%20and%20put%20him%20on%20the%20no-fly%20list.%20Publish%20his%20picture%20so%20people%20are%20aware%20of%20his%20bad%20temper%20in%20public%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20one%20user%20on%20X%2C%20reacting%20to%20the%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20person%20should%20be%20booked%20for%20assault%20as%20well%20as%20put%20on%20a%20No%20Fly%20List.%20While%20%40IndiGo6E%20is%20in%20the%20news%20for%20all%20the%20wrong%20reasons%20and%20must%20be%20taken%20to%20task%20for%20its%20shortcomings%2C%20but%20this%20is%20totally%20unacceptable%20passenger%20behaviour%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20comes%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20significant%20disruptions%20at%20the%20Delhi%20airport%2C%20where%20as%20many%20as%20110%20flights%20experienced%20delays%20and%2079%20flights%20were%20cancelled%20today%2C%20according%20to%20the%20flight%20tracker%20website%20flightradar24.%20The%20average%20delay%20reached%2050%20minutes%2C%20adding%20to%20the%20growing%20frustration%20of%20passengers%20already%20grappling%20with%20extensive%20flight%20disruptions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYesterday%2C%20several%20flights%20arriving%20at%20and%20departing%20from%20the%20Delhi%20airport%20faced%20severe%20delays%2C%20some%20exceeding%20seven%20or%20eight%20hours%2C%20primarily%20due%20to%20adverse%20weather%20conditions%2C%20including%20dense%20fog%2C%20in%20North%20India.%20Major%20airlines%20such%20as%20IndiGo%2C%20SpiceJet%2C%20and%20Vistara%20have%20warned%20that%20ongoing%20bad%20weather%20conditions%20in%20Delhi%20and%20Kolkata%20could%20further%20impact%20flight%20schedules.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705282980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fntg7r2mo_passenger-punches-indigo-pilot_625x300_15_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvideo-passenger-punches-indigo-pilot-announcing-flight-delay-4864612%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20passenger%20aboard%20an%20IndiGo%20flight%20physically%20assaulted%20the%20aircraft's%20pilot%20while%20he%20was%20making%20an%20announcement%20regarding%20delays.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvideo-passenger-punches-indigo-pilot-announcing-flight-delay-4864612%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvideo-passenger-punches-indigo-pilot-announcing-flight-delay-4864612%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvideo-passenger-punches-indigo-pilot-announcing-flight-delay-4864612%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22German%20far-right%20seeks%20to%20piggyback%20on%20farmer%20protests%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705282802000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F109B4%2Fproduction%2F_132302086_tractor.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-67976889%