4e338ec62ab5daf802dfa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22977%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBrandon%20Jones%20and%20Sarah%20Spiro%20built%20a%20floating%20home%20on%20a%20lake.%3Cp%3EBrandon%20Jones%20and%20Sarah%20Spiro%2Fkeepingafloatwiththejoneses%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20complete%20renovation%3A%20While%20the%20roof%20and%20the%20studs%20of%20the%20home%20were%20original%2C%20almost%20everything%20else%20had%20to%20be%20replaced.%20%26quot%3BIt%20wasn't%20livable%20at%20all%2C%20so%20we%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20work%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20Spiro%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20after%20two%20years%2C%20the%20couple%20had%20an%20opportunity%20to%20build%20a%20new%2C%20bigger%20floating%20home%20from%20scratch%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they%20jumped%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20seemed%20like%20a%20win%20for%20us%20because%20we%20could%20size%20up%20slightly%2C%20have%20a%20guest%20room%20and%20a%20place%20to%20host%20our%20friends%20and%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20Spiro%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221458%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20couple%20lounging%20on%20the%20front%20deck%20of%20their%20floating%20home.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6597818eec62ab5daf80e82b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221176%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20couple%20on%20the%20front%20deck%20of%20their%20first%20floating%20home.%3Cp%3EBrandon%20Jones%20and%20Sarah%20Spiro%2Fkeepingafloatwiththejoneses%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20also%20gave%20them%20a%20chance%20to%20rent%20their%20first%2C%20smaller%20floating%20home%20for%20extra%20cash%20%E2%80%94%20which%20they%20did%20for%20one%20summer%20%E2%80%94%20before%20they%20decided%20to%20sell%20it%20off%2C%20she%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20ultimately%20realized%20that%20we're%20just%20not%20landlords.%20It's%20so%20much%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBuilding%20a%20new%20floating%20home%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%2