thing%20at%20the%20store%2C%20there's%20no%20way%20they%20can%20run%20back%20quickly%20to%20get%20it%2C%20Spiro%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20tranquil%20life%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20current%20floating%20home%20%E2%80%94%20although%20larger%20than%20the%20previous%20one%20%E2%80%94%20is%20still%20considered%20a%20tiny%20house.%20Tiny%20houses%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thetinyhouse.net%2Fhow-big-can-a-tiny-house-be%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eusually%20between%2060%20to%20400%20square%20feet%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20one%20thing%20that%20Spiro%20loves%20about%20this%20house%20is%20the%20high%20ceilings%2C%20which%20helps%20open%20up%20the%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20windows%20that%20they%20installed%20all%20around%20the%20home%20also%20mean%20they%20get%20great%20views%20of%20the%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20kitchen.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6594e75fab6f2ebb11f85954%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221170%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20kitchen.%3Cp%3EBrandon%20Jones%20and%20Sarah%20Spiro%2Fkeepingafloatwiththejoneses%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20love%20that%20no%20matter%20what%20you're%20doing%2C%20you%20can%20look%20out%20the%20window%20and%20have%20this%20super%20peaceful%20view%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20you're%20just%20doing%20dishes%2C%26quot%3B%20Spiro%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20she%20admits%20that%20this%20lifestyle%20isn't%20for%20everyone%2C%20it's%20perfect%20for%20her%20and%20Jones%20%E2%80%94%20so%20much%20so%20that%20they%20have%20no%20plans%20to%20go%20back%20to%20living%20in%20a%20normal%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20guess%20it%20depends%20on%20the%20person%2C%20but%20for%20us%2C%20we%20would%20never%20go%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BIt%20beats%20living%20on%20land.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20only%2