r.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20dream%20ride%20didn't%20have%20to%20be%20a%20supercar%20or%20a%20luxury%20model%3B%20I%20just%20wished%20for%20something%20sturdy%2C%20safe%2C%20and%20of%20European%20make%2C%20maybe%20a%20low-end%20Volvo%20or%20Volkswagen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I'm%20in%20Singapore%2C%20frequently%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eiu.com%2Fn%2Fsingapore-and-zurich-top-the-list-as-the-worlds-most-expensive-cities%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DSingapore%2520maintained%2520its%2520pole%2520position%2Cto%2520third%2520place%2520this%2520year.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecrowned%20the%20most%20expensive%20city%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20world%20to%20live%20in%2C%20and%20owning%20a%20car%20is%20turning%20out%20to%20be%20less%20affordable%20for%20me%20than%20owning%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Hyundai%20Avante%2C%20which%20starts%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hyundaiusa.com%2Fus%2Fen%2Fvehicles%2Felantra%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2421%2C475%20in%20the%20US%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20would%20set%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sgcarmart.com%2Fnew_cars%2Fnewcars_overview.php%3FCarCode%3D12749%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eme%20back%20%24135%2C000%20in%20Singapore%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Volkswagen%20Arteon%20with%20a%20starting%20retail%20price%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vw.com%2Fen%2Fmodels%2Farteon.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2443%2C000%20in%20the%20US%3C%2Fa%3E%20costs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sgcarmart.com%2Fnew_cars%2Fnewcars_overview.php%3FCarCode%3D12225%26gad_source%3D1%26gclid%3DCj0KCQiAy9msBhD0ARIsANbk0A8pqBt7v5c3r_iodb_czZQwpCgA0MhQe_g5Al13h4dNcK1TOAYjuygaArrDEALw_wcB%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%24200%2C000%20here%3C%2Fa%3E.%20One%20could%20buy%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yachtworld.com%2Fboats-for-sale%2Fcountry-singapore%2Fprice-100000%2C200000%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E42-foot%20yacht%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20that%20cash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ridiculous%20price%20of%20cars%20in%20Singapore%20stems%20from%20one%20factor%20%E2%80%94%20the%20certificate%20of%20entitlement%2C%20or%20COE.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOld%20men%20in%20coffee%20shops%20curse%20it.%20Millennials%20dread%20it.%20And%20it's%20convinced%20me%2C%20a%20guy%20in%20my%20mid-20s%2C%20to%20abandon%20my%20lifelong%20goal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225184%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Skyscrapers%20and%20traffic%20in%20Singapore.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659b7dfbec62ab5daf81668c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223456%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESkyscrapers%20and%20traffic%20in%20Singapore.%3Cp%3EMikel%20Bilbao%2FVW%20PICS%2FUniversal%20Images%20Group%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EWhy%20a%20simple%20certificate%20could%20cost%20so%20much%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20COE%20is%20a%2010-year%20permit%20for%20a%20vehicle%20to%20be%20driven%20in%20Singapore.%20First%20implemented%20in%201990%2C%20it%20lets%20the%20city-state%20avoid%20traffic%20nightmares%20by%20controlling%20how%20many%20vehicles%20are%20allowed%20on%20the%20roads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20car%20buyers%2C%20the%20COE%20is%20an%20extra%20cost%20that%20can%20easily%20eclipse%20the%20actual%20price%20of%20a%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20it%20works%3A%20Say%20I%20want%20to%20purchase%20a%20%2425%2C000%20brand-new%20sedan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20might%20have%20%2425%2C000%20in%20my%20bank%2C%20but%20first%2C%20I'll%20need%20to%20bid%20for%20a%20COE%2C%20which%20permits%20the%20sedan%20to%20drive%20on%20roads%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20year%2C%20the%20government%20issues%20a%20limited%20number%20of%20vehicle%20certificates.%20These%20are%20put%20up%20for%20competitive%20bidding%2C%20and%20because%20demand%20for%20cars%20is%20always%20high%20in%20Singapore%2C%20I'll%20have%20to%20outbid%20hundreds%20of%20other%20car%20buyers%20and%20their%20dealers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20the%20classic%20demand-and-supply%20theory%20you'd%20learn%20in%20high%20school.%20When%20more%20certificates%20are%20available%2C%20bid%20prices%20go%20down.%20And%20if%20fewer%20certificates%20are%20available%2C%20bid%20prices%20go%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226456%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Demand%20for%20cars%20is%20almost%20always%20high%20in%20Singapore.%20These%20BMW%20family%20cars%20cost%20around%20%24103%2C000%20in%202017.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659ba0e66979d737182125d1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224385%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDemand%20for%20cars%20is%20almost%20always%20high%20in%20Singapore.%20These%20BMW%20family%20cars%20cost%20around%20%24103%2C000%20in%202017.%20That%20red%20sedan%20cost%20%24150%2C000.%3Cp%3EEdgar%20Su%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThey've%20gone%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcoe.sgcharts.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elow%20as%20about%20%249%2C000%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202006%2C%20meaning%20I%20might%20have%20bought%20my%20%2425%2C000%20sedan%20for%20about%20%2436%2C000.%20Not%20too%20bad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20they%20can%20also%20quickly%20surge%20to%20%2470%2C000%2C%20such%20as%20in%202013.%20In%20total%2C%20my%20sedan%20would%20have%20cost%20me%20almost%20quadruple%20the%20retail%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhy%20cars%20are%20so%20expensive%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20drastic%20shifts%20occur%20because%20Singapore%20has%20sometimes%20seen%20huge%20cuts%20and%20bumps%20in%20the%20supply%20of%20certificates%20issued%20yearly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202006%2C%20more%20than%2059%2C000%20certificates%20were%20issued%20for%20cars%20with%20engine%20capacities%20under%201600cc.%20In%202013%2C%20only%208%2C500%20were%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20COE%20bids%20hit%20staggering%20record%20highs%2C%20soaring%20to%20%24113%2C000%20for%20more%20powerful%20cars.%20My%20desired%20%2425%2C000%20sedan%20could%20have%20cost%20me%20upward%20of%20a%20whopping%20%24105%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20another%20catch.%20Even%20if%20I%20could%20afford%20that%20%24105%2C000%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20get%20to%20keep%20the%20car%20forever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20COE%20expires%20when%20it%20hits%20the%2010-year%20mark%2C%20after%20which%20you'll%20have%20to%20buy%20a%20new%20one%20for%20your%20car%20again.%20That%2C%20or%20forfeit%20the%20ability%20to%20drive%20it%20completely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsed%20cars%20have%20inflated%20prices%20as%20well.%20If%20you%20decide%20to%20sell%20your%20ride%20before%20its%20certificate%20expires%2C%20the%20COE%20goes%20along%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20secondhand%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sgcarmart.com%2Fused_cars%2Finfo.php%3FID%3D1260332%26DL%3D2010%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EToyota%20Corolla%20Touring%20Hybrid%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20nine%20years%20left%20on%20the%20clock%2C%20for%20example%2C%20costs%20%24130%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cars%20for%20sale%20are%20parked%20at%20used%20car%20dealerships%20in%20Singapore%20October%2017%2C%202022.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659ba3c16979d737182125f3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECars%20for%20sale%20are%20parked%20at%20used%20car%20dealerships%20in%20Singapore%20October%2017%2C%202022.%20COE%20prices%20went%20up%20to%20%2467%2C000%20that%20year%20for%20lower-end%20cars%2C%20despite%20more%20than%2013%2C000%20certificates%20being%20made%20available.%3Cp%3EEDGAR%20SU%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bottom%20line%20is%20that%20the%20COE%20is%20inescapable%20if%20you%20want%20to%20buy%20a%20car%20in%20Singapore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWalter%20Theseira%2C%20associate%20professor%20of%20Economics%20at%20the%20Singapore%20University%20of%20Social%20Sciences%2C%20told%20me%20that%20he%20predicts%20bid%20prices%20will%20become%20far%20cheaper%20in%20about%20five%20years%20due%20to%20market%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20signs%20of%20a%20decline%20are%20showing.%20On%20Thursday%2C%20COE%20prices%20for%20lower-end%20cars%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.channelnewsasia.com%2Fsingapore%2Fcoe-premiums-cars-drop-jan-4-2024-4024796%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efell%20to%20about%20%2448%2C000%2C%20a%20steep%20drop%20that%20shocked%20the%20market%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.todayonline.com%2Fsingapore%2Flookahead-2024-coe-prices-moderate-private-car-sharing-costs-may-rise-2336356%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EExperts%20say%20bids%20should%3C%2Fa%3E%20bounce%20back%20shortly%20as%20people%20rush%20to%20buy%20cars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20even%20in%20the%20best%20years%20for%20buyers%2C%20bid%20levels%20have%20rivaled%20the%20entire%20cost%20of%20a%20car.%20In%202019%2C%20when%20prices%20dropped%20to%20their%20lowest%20in%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20most%20bids%20still%20hovered%20at%20%2425%2C000%20per%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20a%20significant%20investment%20in%20a%20metropolis%20where%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.straitstimes.com%2Fsingapore%2Fjobs%2Freal-median-income-in-singapore-falls-23-in-2023-on-high-inflation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emedian%20income%20is%20%243%2C900%3C%2Fa%3E.%20An%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.todayonline.com%2Fbig-read%2Fbig-read-short-what-drives-singaporeans-car-owning-dreams-amid-soaring-coe-prices-2281466%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOctober%20analysis%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20car%20ownership%20by%20local%20news%20outlet%20TODAY%20found%20that%20car%20owners.%20This%20means%20those%20wealthy%20enough%20to%20afford%20a%20COE%20typically%20spend%20around%2030%25%20of%20their%20monthly%20income%20on%20car%20expenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompare%20that%20to%20Americans%20spending%20an%20average%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.energy.gov%2Feere%2Fvehicles%2Farticles%2Ffotw-1248-july-25-2022-average-us-household-spent-nearly-10000%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20of%2016%25%20of%20their%20household%20expenses%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20doesn't%20include%20their%20savings%2C%20on%20cars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20other%20big%20responsibilities%20beckon%2C%20like%20buying%20a%20home%20before%20I'm%2040.%20It's%20possible%20for%20most%20Singaporeans%2C%20even%20in%20such%20a%20dense%20nation.%20Nearly%2090%25%20of%20Singaporeans%20live%20in%20homes%20that%20they%20own%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.singstat.gov.sg%2Ffind-data%2Fsearch-by-theme%2Fhouseholds%2Fhouseholds%2Flatest-data%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egovernment%20statistics.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESo%20what's%20the%20alternative%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESingapore's%20government%20is%20keenly%20aware%20that%20if%20it%20wants%20to%20curb%20car%20ownership%2C%20it%20has%20to%20offer%20an%20alternative%20for%20commuters%2C%20said%20Theseira%2C%20whose%20research%20focuses%20on%20transport%20economics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20sprawling%20city%20like%20Singapore%2C%20public%20transport%20is%20the%20obvious%20choice.%20Getting%20people%20to%20take%20the%20bus%20or%20train%20has%20its%20allure%20for%20every%20city%20government%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20good%20for%20the%20environment%2C%20cost-efficient%2C%20and%20creates%20far%20less%20traffic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20downsides%20are%20plenty%2C%20of%20course.%20Getting%20out%20and%20about%20brings%20discomfort.%20Singapore%20is%20unceasingly%20humid%2C%20with%20regular%2086-degree%20heat%20and%20brutal%20thunderstorms%20that%20seemingly%20invade%20the%20skies%20out%20of%20nowhere.%20The%20subway%20takes%20me%20double%20or%20triple%20the%20time%20to%20reach%20my%20destination%20compared%20to%20if%20I%20drive%2C%20even%20though%20Singapore's%20only%20half%20the%20size%20of%20New%20York%20City.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20there's%20a%20lot%20to%20look%20forward%20to%20for%20someone%20who%20doesn't%20intend%20to%20own%20a%20car%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%2020%20years%2C%20Singapore%20has%20poured%20funds%20into%20its%20subways%20and%20buses%2C%20pivoting%20away%20from%20its%20reliance%20on%20passenger%20fares%20to%20pay%20for%20public%20transport.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20been%20in%20the%20business%20of%20encouraging%20people%20to%20take%20public%20transport%20for%20years%20because%20we%20know%20driving%20or%20taking%20a%20motorbike%20just%20isn't%20sustainable%2C%26quot%3B%20Theseira%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20the%20effort%20to%20do%20this%20really%20kicked%20into%20high%20gear%20in%20the%20last%20one%20or%20two%20decades.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Taking%20public%20transport%20has%20been%20a%20norm%20for%20decades%20in%20Singapore%2C%20but%20might%20soon%20become%20the%20only%20real%20option%20for%20those%20who%20aren't%20wealthy.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659b9e711c5c7b8c9a0eb055%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETaking%20public%20transport%20has%20been%20a%20norm%20for%20decades%20in%20Singapore%2C%20but%20might%20soon%20become%20the%20only%20real%20option%20for%20those%20who%20aren't%20wealthy.%3Cp%3EROSLAN%20RAHMAN%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESingapore%20has%20invested%20at%20least%20%24113%20billion%20into%20its%20subway%20system%20since%20the%20late%201980s.%20On%20some%20recent%20projects%2C%20we've%20spent%20up%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftransitcosts.com%2Fsingapore-circle-line-stage-6%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%241.3%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20every%20mile%20of%20railway%20built%2C%20per%20transit%20project%20tracker%20Transit%20Costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20more%20expensive%20than%20any%20subway%20project%20in%20Tokyo%2C%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftransitcosts.com%2Ftokyo-sotetsu-shin-yokohama-jr-line%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESotetsu%20Shin-