nth's%20poll%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20the%20former%20president%20earned%2051%25%20support%20among%20GOP%20caucusgoers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20final%20GOP%20caucus%20poll%20still%20shows%20Trump%20nearly%2030%20points%20ahead%20of%20Haley%2C%20and%20the%20former%20president%20has%20majority%20support%20among%20both%20first-time%20caucusgoers%20(56%25)%20and%20evangelical%20Christians%20(51%25)%20%E2%80%94%20with%20a%20stratospheric%2088%25%20of%20his%20supporters%20stating%20that%20they're%20extremely%20enthusiastic%20about%20his%20candidacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20is%20in%20the%20best%20position%20he's%20ever%20been%20in%20for%20a%20contested%20GOP%20caucus%20in%20Iowa.%20The%202016%20caucus%20results%20provide%20a%20measure%20of%20just%20how%20much%20the%20former%20president%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdesantis-trump-iowa-caucuses-standing-2024-gop-presidential-race-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20throttled%20his%20competition%20this%20time%20around%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20does%20Trump's%20standing%20compare%20to%202016%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20Trump%20was%20still%20new%20to%20GOP%20politics%2C%20but%20he%20needed%20no%20introduction%20to%20the%20American%20public%20after%20his%20years%20as%20a%20celebrity%20businessman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%20glance%2C%20Trump's%20brash%20personality%20seemed%20ill-suited%20for%20Iowa%2C%20known%20for%20its%20Midwestern%20sensibilities%20and%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fiowa-democrats-struggling-ascendant-gop-2024-presidential-race-trump-biden-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Euntil%20recently%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20its%20status%20as%20one%20of%20the%20nation's%20most%20recognizable%20swing%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ted%20Cruz%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a42a7c43bb77284b9d08a4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20he