haracter's%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Epic%20Games%20doesn't%20have%20the%20funds%20to%20animate%20Peter%20Griffin%2C%20it%20certainly%20isn't%20because%20it's%20losing%20money%20in%20court.%20The%20video%20game%20company%20recently%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-loses-app-store-antitrust-suit-against-fortnite-creators-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewon%20a%20landmark%20civil%20case%20against%20Google%20involving%3C%2Fa%3E%20Fortnite.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEpic%20Games%20sued%20Google%20after%20Fortnite%20was%20banned%20from%20the%20Google%20Play%20Store%20because%20Epic%20allowed%20users%20to%20buy%20in-game%20features%20from%20the%20game%20developer%20directly%2C%20avoiding%20Google's%20fees%20on%20in-app%20purchases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2011%2C%20a%20jury%20found%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-lawsuit-antitrust-case-doj-search-agreements-apple-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EGoogle%20held%20a%20monopoly%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20its%20Play%20Store%2C%20limiting%20the%20reach%20of%20competitors'%20apps%20and%20charging%20high%20fees%20for%20processing%20in-app%20purchases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMacFarlane%20said%20when%20he%20was%20originally%20approached%20about%20adding%20Peter%20to%20the%20game%2C%20he%20didn't%20know%20what%20Fortnite%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20to%20have%20somebody%20explain%20to%20me%20what%20the%20fuck%20Fortnite%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20MacFarlane%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20I%20said%2C%20'Well%2C%20that%20sounds%20kind%20of%20cool.'%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMacFarlane%20notably%20did%20not%20voice%20Peter%20in%20the%20promotional%20video%20released%20by%20Epic%20Games%20showing%20his%20encounter%20with%20Meowscles%2C%20in%20which%20Peter%20has%20no%20voice%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessin