%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Ffinance%2Fnews%2Finterim-budget-may-raise-pension-floor-for-unorganised-sector-workers-124011400257_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2276th%20Army%20Day%20Parade%20Today%20In%20Lucknow%2C%20What%20Makes%20It%20Special%20This%20Year%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Army%20will%20celebrate%20the%2076th%20Army%20Day%20with%20a%20grand%20parade%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20capital%20city%2C%20Lucknow%2C%20today.%20The%20Army%20Day%20parade%20has%20been%20moved%20out%20of%20Delhi%20for%20the%20second%20consecutive%20year.%20Last%20year%2C%20the%20parade%20took%20place%20at%20Bengaluru's%20MED%20%26amp%3B%20Centre's%20Parade%20Ground.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDefence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20and%20Governor%20Anandi%20Ben%20Patel%20will%20be%20in%20attendance%20as%20chief%20guests%20at%20the%20parade%20ground%20in%20Lucknow.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Army%20Day%20Is%20Celebrated%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArmy%20Day%20is%20celebrated%20every%20year%20on%20January%2015%20to%20commemorate%20the%20occasion%20when%20General%20(Later%20Field%20Marshal)%20KM%20Cariappa%20took%20charge%20of%20the%20Indian%20Army%20from%20General%20Sir%20Francis%20Roy%20Bucher%20in%201949%20and%20became%20the%20first-ever%20Indian%20to%20command%20the%20Army%20in%20its%20long%2C%20rich%20history.%20General%20Sir%20Francis%20Roy%20Bucher%20was%20the%20last%20British-serving%20chief%20of%20the%20Indian%20Army.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EField%20Marshal%20KM%20Cariappa%2C%20known%20as%20'Kipper'%2C%20received%20his%20King's%20Commission%20in%201919%20and%20was%20part%20of%20the%20first%20group%20of%20Indian%20cadets%20at%20the%20Royal%20Military%20College%20in%20Sandhurst%2C%20UK.%20Field%20Marshal%20Cariappa%20was%20the%20first%20Indian%20to%20attend%20the%20Staff%20College%20in%20Quetta%20and%20the%20first%20Indian%20to%20command%20a%20Batallion.%20In%201942%2C%20he%20raised%20the%207th%20Rajput%20Machine%20Gun%20Batallion%2C%20later%20known%20as%2017%20Rajput.%20In%201986%2C%20KM%20Cariappa%20was%20conferred%20with%20the%20rank%20of%20Field%20Marshal.%20He%20died%20at%20the%20age%20of%2094%20in%201993.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Field%20Marshal%20Kodandera%20Madappa%20Cariappa%2C%20OBE%20%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Field%20Marshal%20Kodandera%20Madappa%20Cariappa%2C%20OBE%20%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fshg49b3g_km-cariappa_625x300_14_January_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EField%20Marshal%20Kodandera%20Madappa%20Cariappa%2C%20OBE%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%201949%20till%202022%2C%20the%20Army%20Day%20parade%20was%20organised%20at%20the%20Cariappa%20Parade%20Ground%20in%20the%20Delhi%20Cantonment.%20The%20Chief%20of%20Army%20Staff%20reviews%20the%20marching%20contingents%20who%20also%20take%20part%20in%20the%20Republic%20Day%20Parade%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20the%20parade%20will%20be%20held%20under%20the%20Command%20of%20Army's%20'Central%20Command%2C%20which%20is%20headquartered%20in%20Lucknow.%20Central%20Command%20is%20one%20of%20the%20seven%20operational%20commands%20of%20the%20Indian%20Army.%20Last%20year%2C%20the%20Southern%20Command%20was%20responsible%20for%20the%20parade%20in%20Bengaluru.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGrand%20Spectacle%20In%20Lucknow%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20grand%20spectacle%20will%20take%20place%20at%20the%20parade%20ground%20of%20the%2011%20Gorkha%20Rifles%20Regimental%20Centre%20in%20Lucknow%20under%20the%20command%20of%20Major%20General%20Salil%20Seth.%20Six%20marching%20contingents%20from%20the%20army's%20different%20regiments%2C%20a%20military%20band%20comprising%20five%20regimental%20brass%20bands%20and%20three%20pipe%20bands%20will%20participate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E50th%20(Independent)%20Parachute%20Brigade%2C%20Sikh%20Light%20Infantry%2C%20Jat%20Regiment%2C%20Garhwal%20Rifles%2C%20Bengal%20Engineer%20Group%20and%20the%20Army%20Air%20Defence%20contingent%20march%20down%20the%20parade%20ground.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20five%20regimental%20brass%2Fmilitary%20bands%20are%20-%20Punjab%20Regiment%20Centre%2C%20Grenadier%20Regimental%20Centre%2C%20Bihar%20Regiment%20Centre%2C%20Sikh%20Light%20Regiment%20Centre%2C%20Kumaon%20Regimental%20Centre%20and%20SIKH%20Regimental%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20five%20regimental%20pipe%20bands%20are%20the%20SIKH%20Regiment%20Centre%2C%20SIKH%20LI%20Regiment%20Centre%2C%20JAT%20Regiment%20Centre%2C%20KUMAON%20Regimental%20Centre%20and%201%20Signal%20Training%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArmy%20chief%20General%20Manoj%20Pande%20will%20review%20the%20parade%20and%20present%20gallantry%20awards%2C%20which%20will%20be%20followed%20by%20a%20daring%20motorcycle%20display%20by%20the%20Army%20Service%20Corps%20(ASC)%20Tornadoes%2C%20a%20skydiving%20display%20by%20the%20Paratroopers%2C%20daredevil%20jumps%2C%20and%20a%20fly%20past%20by%20of%20helicopters%20of%20the%20Army%20Aviation%20Corps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EUse%20Of%20AI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year's%20Army%20Day%20parade%20will%20be%20special%20because%20of%20the%20use%20of%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20to%20select%20the%20'Best%20Marching%20Contingent'.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BArtificial%20Intelligence%20is%20being%20used%20for%20the%20first%20time%20to%20identify%20the%20best%20marching%20contingent%2C%26quot%3B%20Major%20General%20Salil%20Seth%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20marching%20contingents%20do%20drills%20but%20there%20is%20a%20pattern%20of%20doing%20it%20--%20raising%20your%20hands%20and%20legs%20to%20a%20certain%20level%20and%20doing%20your%20movement%20with%20the%20weapon%20within%20a%20certain%20timeframe.%20We%20will%20capture%20the%20individual%20movement%20with%20a%20camera%20and%20then%20the%20computer%20software%20using%20the%20AI%20will%20give