eforms%2030%20years%20ago%2C%20is%20a%20party%20that%20is%20abusing%20industrialists%2C%20businessmen%20and%20calling%20businessmen%20'anti-nationals'%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said%20earlier%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20to%20NDTV%2C%20Mr%20Deora%20expanded%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20father%20told%20me%20to%20speak%20well%20on%20Day%20One%20of%20politics%E2%80%A6%20It%20is%20about%20working%20with%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Prime%20Minister%20Manmohan%20Singh%2C%20who%20brought%20the%201991%20reforms%2C%20%26quot%3Bnever%20named%20industrialists%20and%20attacked%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Deora%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20(Manmohan%20Singh)%20questioned%20institutions.%20The%20Congress%20is%20personally%20attacking%20businessmen.%20It%20is%20very%20sad%20that%20party%20that%20was%20great%20once%20has%20gone%20down%20to%20a%20level%20of%20calling%20people%20names%20and%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20names.%20I've%20never%20made%20such%20statements%20in%20my%2020%20years%20of%20politics%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Deora%2C%20who%20was%20upset%20over%20the%20Thackeray%20faction%20laying%20claim%20over%20the%20Mumbai%20South%20seat%2C%20occupied%20by%20his%20father%20and%20then%20him%2C%20said%20Eknath%20Shinde%20has%20assured%20him%20that%20he%20could%20be%20an%20MP%20from%20Mumbai%20or%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnfortunately%2C%20the%20Congress%20didn't%20believe%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BHe%20(Mr%20Shinde)%20invited%20me%20to%20the%20party%20so%20that%20I%20could%20guide%20them.%20I%20want%20to%20do%20positive%20politics%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20also%20upset%20over%20the%20party's%20apparent%20lack%20of%20reaction%20to%20Sena%20UBT%20leader%20Sanjay%20Raut's%20provocative%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20did%20express%20regret%20over%20statemen