harity%20shared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMatt%20admitted%20to%20dating%20another%20woman%20for%20two%20months.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20soon%20decided%20to%20take%20the%20path%20of%20divorce.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20thought%20I%20knew%20my%20husband%20better%20than%20anyone%20else%2C%20but%20he'd%20been%20living%20a%20double%20life%20and%20I%20had%20no%20idea%2C%26quot%3B%20Charity%20lamented.%20%26quot%3BMy%20whole%20world%20was%20turned%20upside%20down%2C%20and%20I%20didn't%20know%20how%20I'd%20ever%20recover.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Matt%20moved%20on%20with%20another%20woman%2C%20Mrs%20Craig%20visited%20a%20counsellor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20few%20sessions%2C%20she%20learned%20that%20Matt's%20affair%20was%20not%20the%20only%20reason%20for%20their%20marital%20problems.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20started%20therapy%2C%20and%20I%20realized%20that%20I%20was%20no%20longer%20the%20woman%20he'd%20married%2C%20and%20he%20wasn't%20solely%20to%20blame%20for%20the%20breakdown%20of%20our%20relationship%2C%26quot%3B%20Charity%20recalled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20spent%20eight%20months%20working%20on%20myself%20-%20building%20up%20my%20self-confidence%20and%20learning%20how%20to%20deal%20with%20my%20problems%20healthily%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20shared%20that%20they%20got%20back%20together%20in%20February%202013%20after%20undergoing%20couple%20counselling.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20just%20that%2C%20Matt%20also%20gave%20Charity%20all%20the%20passwords%20to%20his%20social%20media%20and%20phone.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BMatt%20was%20incredibly%20sorry%20for%20the%20affair%2C%20but%20I%20was%20also%20sorry%20for%20my%20part%20in%20the%20breakdown%20of%20our%20marriage%2C%26quot%3B%20Charity%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20had%20to%20completely%20start%20again%2C%20but%20it%20was%20worth%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Charity%20works%20as%20a%20marriage%20counsellor%20to%20help%20other%20couples%20struggling%20after%20an%20affair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20hard%20work%2C%20but%20so%20rewarding%20to%20help%20other%20couples%20move%20past%20betrayal%20and%20rebuild%20their%20marriage%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20mom%20of%20four%20declared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%2C%20after%20the%20story%20of%20the%20couple%20went%20viral.%20In%20the%20comments%20section%2C%20many%20people%20expressed%20concern%20about%20their%20relationship.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20gonna%20do%20it%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20user%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBro%20looks%20happy%20to%20have%20made%20it%20thru.%20Forgiveness.%20It%20can%20work%20wonders!%20If%20the%20lesson%20was%20learned%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20user%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWait%20until%20she%20finds%20out%20he's%20gay%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20third%20user%20commented.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705244400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fnerr7fu_matt-craig_625x300_14_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fus-woman-claims-she-caught-her-husband-cheating-and-it-saved-their-marriage-internet-in-disbelief-4862405%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mrs%20Craig%20revealed%20that%20her%20husband%2C%20Matt%2C%20left%20the%20home%20to%20continue%20his%20relationship%20with%20the%20other%20woman.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fus-woman-claims-she-caught-her-husband-cheating-and-it-saved-their-marriage-internet-in-disbelief-4862405%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fus-woman-claims-she-caught-her-husband-cheating-and-it-saved-their-marriage-internet-in-disbelief-4862405%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fus-woman-claims-she-caught-her-husband-cheating-and-it-saved-their-marriage-inte