the%20first%20meeting%20began%20in%20Male%2C%20with%20the%20Indian%20side%20represented%20by%20India%E2%80%99s%20high%20commissioner%20Munu%20Mahawar%2C%20MEA%20joint%20secretary%20Puneet%20Aggarwal%20and%20senior%20defence%20ministry%20officials.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Maldivian%20officials%20at%20the%20table%20included%20Chief%20of%20Staff%20of%20the%20President%E2%80%99s%20Office%20Abdulla%20Fayaz%2C%20Ambassador%20at%20Large%20for%20foreign%20ministry%2C%20Ali%20Naseer%2C%20Maldives%20Ambassador%20to%20India%2C%20Ibrahim%20Shaheeb%20and%20Chief%20of%20Defence%20Force%20Abdul%20Raheem%20Abdul%20Latheef%2C%20as%20per%20local%20media%20reports.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELater%20in%20the%20day%2C%20the%20public%20policy%20secretary%20at%20the%20President%E2%80%99s%20Office%2C%20Abdulla%20Nazim%20Ibrahim%20announced%20that%20President%20Muizzu%20has%20officially%20requested%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20Indian%20military%20personnel%20by%20March%2015.%20This%20was%20made%20clear%20at%20the%20meeting%20underway%20at%20the%20Maldivian%20capital.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpsmnews.mv%2Fen%2F131583%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20Maldivian%20state%20media%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Ibrahim%20said%20that%20the%20Cabinet%20had%20received%20the%20latest%20information%20on%20the%20Indian%20military%20personnel%20stationed%20in%20the%20Maldives.%20Around%2088%20Indian%20military%20personnel%20are%20reportedly%20based%20in%20Maldives.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Maldivian%20official%20also%20claimed%20that%20the%20two%20countries%20have%20held%20%E2%80%9C12%20meetings%20on%20the%20issue%20so%20far%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20readout%20of%20the%20meeting%2C%20issued%20on%20Sunday%20evening%2C%20did%20not%20mention%20the%20deadline%20provided%20by%20Maldives.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2