of%20this%2C%20Lakshadweep%20at%20this%20time%20is%20looking%20at%20%26quot%3Bhigh-end%20controlled%20tourism%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20where%20the%20union%20territory%20plans%20to%20raise%20maximum%20revenue%20from%20very%20controlled%20tourism.%20The%20tourists%20who%20come%20in%20also%20have%20to%20give%20%26quot%3Bconsent%20towards%20environment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%2010%20of%20Lakshadweep's%2036%20islands%20are%20inhabited.%20Currently%20only%208-10%20per%20cent%20of%20Lakshadweep's%20population%20depends%20on%20tourism.%20The%20islands%20were%20not%20on%20the%20list%20of%20many%20people%20either.%20But%20with%20the%20row%20with%20Maldives%2C%20many%20on%20social%20media%20are%20declaring%20that%20Laskshadweep%20will%20be%20their%20next%20destination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20diplomatic%20row%20started%20as%20Maldivian%20ministers%20made%20derogatory%20comments%20following%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20widely%20circulated%20post%20about%20his%20visit%20to%20the%20Lakshadweep%20islands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20Maldivian%20ministers%20were%20sacked%20and%20the%20country's%20Opposition%20criticised%20the%20comments.%20But%20Maldivian%20President%20Mohamed%20Muizzu%20was%20defiant%20and%20it%20gave%20a%20frsh%20boost%20to%20the%20country's%20ties%20with%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%20the%20Maldives%20President%20gave%20a%20deadline%20to%20India%20to%20withdraw%20its%20troops%20from%20the%20island%20nation.%20The%20Indian%20military%20personnel%20should%20leave%20the%20nation%20by%20March%2015%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705242480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F2r43oqr8_lakshadweep-mmt_625x300_08_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flakshadweep-can-never-handle-a-major-tourist-influx-mp-explains-why-4862216%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20%26quot%3BChalo%20Lakshadweep%26quot%3B%20call%20on%20Indian%20social%20medi