ay%203%2C%202023%20in%20which%20over%20170%20people%20have%20lost%20their%20lives%20and%20tens%20of%20thousands%20have%20been%20displaced%20from%20their%20homes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGandhi%2C%20who%20started%20the%20yatra%20by%20first%20paying%20tributes%20at%20the%20Khongjom%20War%20Memorial%20in%20Thoubal%2C%20said%20that%20when%20the%20Congress%20party%20was%20deliberating%20upon%20where%20to%20begin%20the%20second%20instalment%20of%20the%20yatra%2C%20which%20has%20been%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-renames-rahul-gandhis-bharat-nyay-yatra-as-bharat-jodo-nyay-yatra%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Erechristened%20as%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20answer%20was%20clear%20to%20him.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F14194535%2FVolunteer-stalls-outside-public-meeting-venue-in-Thoubal-Manipur-asking-people-to-join-the-yatra-by-giving-missed-calls.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F14194535%2FVolunteer-stalls-outside-public-meeting-venue-in-Thoubal-Manipur-asking-people-to-join-the-yatra-by-giving-missed-calls.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F14194535%2FVolunteer-stalls-outside-public-meeting-venue-in-Thoubal-Manipur-asking-people-to-join-the-yatra-by-giving-missed-calls-300x225.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-692953%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EVolunteer%20stalls%20outside%20public%20meeting%20venue%20in%20Thoubal%20Manipur%20asking%20people%20to%20join%20the%20yatra%20by%20giving%20missed%20calls.%20Photo%3A%20Sravasti%20Dasgupta%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20question%20came%20up%20about%20where%20to%20start%20this%20yatra%2C%20some%20suggested%20east%20some%20suggested%20west.%20But%20it%20was%20clear%20to%20me%20that%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20can%20only%20start%20from%20Manipur%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGandhi%20said%20that%20the%20continued%20violence%20in%20the%20state%20shows%20that%20the%20state%20is%20an%20example%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)-RSS%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%9Cideology%20of%20hate.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CManipur%20is%20an%20example%20of%20the%20BJP-RSS%E2%80%99%20ideology%20of%20hate.%20Yes%2C%20you%E2%80%99ve%20lost%20what%20you%20valued%20but%20we%20will%20find%20it%20back.%20We%20understand%20the%20pain%20and%20hurt%20and%20loss%20sadness%20that%20people%20of%20Manipur%20have%20been%20through.%20We%20promise%20you%20and%20commit%20to%20you%20that%20we%20will%20bring%20what%20you%20value%2C%20the%20harmony%2C%20peace%20and%20affection%20that%20this%20state%20is%20known%20for%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20north-south%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20was%20conducted%20from%20October%202022%20to%20January%202023%20from%20Kanyakumari%20to%20Kashmir%2C%20the%20present%20leg%20will%20be%20an%20east%20to%20west%20yatra%20that%20will%20go%20from%20Manipur%20to%20Mumbai%20and%20end%20in%20March.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20yatra%20was%20earlier%20expected%20to%20begin%20from%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20capital%20Imphal%20but%20was%20moved%20to%20a%20private%20ground%20in%20Thoubal%20after%20the%20BJP%20state%20government%20refused%20to%20provide%20permission%20for%20a%20public%20rally%20in%20Imphal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGandhi%20said%20that%20yatra%20will%20raise%20issues%20about%20economic%2C%20political%20and%20social%20inequalities%20as%20India%20is%20going%20through%20a%20period%20of%20%E2%80%9Cinjustice.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20less%20about%20us%20and%20more%20about%20you.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20tell%20you%20our%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emann%20ki%20baat.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20want%20to%20listen%20to%20yours.%20And%20together%20with%20you%20the%20vision%20of%20India%20will%20not%20be%20of%20violence%20hatred%2C%20monopoly%20but%20of%20harmonious%20equitable%20and%20brotherhood%20vision%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20yatra%20will%20cover%206%2C700%20km%20and%20touch%20110%20districts%2C%20100%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20and%20337%20assembly%20constituencies%20in%20what%20is%20the%20biggest%20mass%20outreach%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20on%20Saturday%2C%20Congress%20MP%20and%20general%20secretary%20in-charge%20media%20and%20communication%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20said%20to%20reporters%20in%20Imphal%20that%20the%20yatra%20will%20be%20political%20but%20not%20electoral.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20not%20an%20electoral%20yatra%2C%20it%20is%20an%20ideological%20yatra.%20It%20is%20a%20political%20rally%20by%20a%20political%20party.%20There%20is%20a%20political%20purpose%20to%20protect%20the%20constitution.%20But%20not%20to%20discuss%20seats%20and%20impact%20on%20seats%20(for%20the%20elections)%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERamesh%20said%20that%20the%20decision%20to%20start%20from%20Manipur%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdeliberate%20choice%E2%80%9D%20as%20the%20prime%20minister%20is%20yet%20to%20visit%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20bigger%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eanyay%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(injustice)%20than%20this%20to%20Manipur.%20The%20tensions%20in%20the%20last%20eight%20months%20in%20which%20lakhs%20have%20been%20displaced%20and%20many%20have%20lost%20their%20lives%20yet%20he%20has%20not%20broken%20his%20silence.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CManipur%20has%20gone%20through%20agony%2C%20social%20harmony%20has%20been%20disturbed.%20This%20was%20going%20to%20be%20an%20east%20to%20west%20yatra.%20But%20we%20decided%20to%20start%20from%20Manipur%20to%20highlight%20what%20has%20been%20going%20on%20and%20to%20highlight%20that%20the%20PM%20has%20not%20met%20anyone%20from%20the%20state%20yet.%20We%20are%20hoping%20people%20of%20Manipur%20will%20see%20this%20difference%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKharge%20also%20took%20aim%20at%20Modi%20for%20not%20visiting%20Manipur%20and%20accused%20him%20of%20chanting%20the%20name%20of%20Ram%20while%20carrying%20hatred.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20(the%20PM)%20always%20comes%20here%20for%20votes.%20But%20when%20people%20of%20Manipur%20were%20suffering%20and%20facing%20violence%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20did%20not%20bother%20to%20visit%20them%20even%20once%20while%20he%20had%20all%20the%20time%20to%20roam%20on%20the%20beaches%20and%20go%20snorkelling%20into%20the%20sea%20and%20sit%20and%20chant%20%E2%80%98Ram%20Ram%E2%80%99.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMukh%20mein%20Ram%2C%20bagal%20mein%20choori%20mat%20karo%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3EDon%E2%80%99t%20chant%20the%20name%20of%20Ram%20and%20keep%20a%20knife%20on%20your%20side)%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20peace%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELocals%20who%20had%20come%20to%20the%20venue%20in%20Khongjom%2C%20Thoubal%2C%20said%20that%20he%20had%20come%20for%20%E2%80%9Cpeace%20and%20harmony.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThombi%2C%20an%20elderly%20woman%2C%20who%20had%20come%20from%20a%20village%20about%2020%20kms%20from%20Khongjom%20along%20with%20two%20other%20women%20from%20her%20village%20said%20that%20she%20had%20come%20to%20see%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20see%20peace%20and%20harmony%20and%20hear%20what%20he%20has%20to%20say%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F14194620%2FThombi-left-corner-who-had-come-from-a-village-about-20kms-Khongjom-to-the-yatra.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F14194620%2FThombi-left-corner-who-had-come-from-a-village-about-20kms-Khongjom-to-the-yatra.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F14194620%2FThombi-left-corner-who-had-come-from-a-village-about-20kms-Khongjom-to-the-yatra-300x225.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-692954%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThombi%20(left%20corner)%20who%20had%20come%20from%20a%20village%20about%2020kms%20Khongjom%20to%20the%20yatra.%20Photo%3A%20Sravasti%20Dasguptaripla%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20former%20defence%20personnel%2C%20N.D.%20Singh%2C%20also%20a%20resident%20of%20Thoubal%20said%20that%20whether%20it%20is%20the%20Congress%20or%20the%20BJP-they%20should%20look%20at%20Manipur%20through%20the%20lens%20of%20humanity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CNo%20one%20cares%20about%20what%20has%20been%20happening%20here%20for%20the%20last%20eight%20months.%20Everyone%20in%20Manipur%20will%20tell%20you%20what%E2%80%99s%20going%20on%20yet%20no%20one%20cares.%20The%20prime%20minister%20has%20not%20come%20here%2C%20the%20home%20minister%20has%20come%20only%20once.%20Whether%20it%20is%20BJP%20or%20Congress%20they%20should%20look%20at%20us%20through%20the%20lens%20of%20humanity%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20cannot%20think%20of%20a%20better%20way%20to%20counter%20the%20politics%20of%20otherness%20than%20the%20song-%20apne%20ho%20ya%20paraye%20sabke%20liye%20ho%20nyay.%20That%20very%20much%20is%20the%20spirit%20that%20informs%20this%20yatra.%20We%20are%20not%20from%20Congress%20and%20we%20represent%20people%E2%80%99s%20movements.%20Why%20we%20support%20this%20is%20because%20a%20call%20for%20nyay%20is%20so%20desperately%20needed%20because%20Manipur%20is%20the%20right%20place%20as%20it%20represents%20the%20grossest%20injustices%20in%20independent%20India.%20In%20rest%20of%20the%20country%20there%20is%20such%20ignorance%20about%20Manipur.%20We%20hope%20this%20yatra%20will%20bring%20light%20to%20the%20true%20character%20of%20this%20place%2C%20its%20deep%20diversity%20and%20the%20role%20of%20its%20women%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20celebrated%2C%E2%80%9D%20political%20activist%20Yogendra%20Yadav%20said%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ehas%20learnt%20that%20during%20his%20stay%20in%20Manipur%20on%20Sunday%20and%20Monday%2C%20Gandhi%20will%20meet%20both%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki%20groups.%20While%20he%20is%20expected%20to%20meet%20the%20Meitei%20groups%20around%20Imphal%2C%20he%20will%20meet%20the%20Kuki%20groups%20as%20he%20makes%20his%20way%20towards%20Nagaland%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhether%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20message%20of%20unity%20and%20brotherhood%20will%20permeate%20to%20the%20conflict%20struck%20state%20however%20is%20still%20not%20clear.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20positive%20message%20that%20he%20is%20starting%20his%20yatra%20from%20Manipur%20and%20talking%20about%20peace%20but%20it%20may%20not%20help%20de-escalate%20the%20situation%20without%20the%20state%20and%20central%20government%E2%80%99s%20support.%20The%20people%20need%20government%20intervention%20to%20bring%20peace.%20Once%20the%20government%20steps%20in%2C%20especially%20the%20central%20government%2C%20and%20takes%20decisive%20measures%20to%20bring%20peace%20between%20the%20two%20communities%20then%20it%20will%20help%20calm%20tensions%20in%20the%20state%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20young%20graduate%20who%20had%20come%20to%20attend%20the%20yatra%20but%20did%20not%20wish%20to%20be%20named%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705242012000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F16140758%2F325789683_3090620014563969_3138271416364092009_n.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpromise-to-bring-peace-says-rahul-gandhi-as-he-kicks-off-bharat-jodo-nyay-yatra-from-manipur%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20yatra%20will%20cover%206%2C700%20km%20from%20Thoubal%2C%20Manipur%20to%20Mumbai%20and%20touch%20110%20districts%2C%20100%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20and%20337%20assembly%20constituencies%20in%20what%20is%20the%20biggest%20mass%20outreach%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpromise-to-bring-peace-says-rahul-gandhi-as-he-kicks-off-bharat-jodo-nyay-yatra-from-manipur%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Pictures%3A%20Denmark's%20beloved%20Queen%20bows%20out%2C%20new%20King%20is%20proclaimed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705241520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F01%2F768x432%2Fskynews-denmark-king-frederik_6421328.jpg%3F20240114143346%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fdenmarks-queen-margrethe-ii-bows-out-new-king-frederik-x-is-proclaimed-13048244%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Denmark's%20King%20Frederik%20X%20has%20been%20proclaimed%20as%C2%A0the%20new%20head%20of%20Europe's%20oldest%20monarchy%20during%20a%20day%20of%20pomp%20in%20Copenhagen.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A110%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fdenmarks-queen-margrethe-ii-bows-out-new-king-frederik-x-is-proclaimed-13048244%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fdenmarks-queen-margrethe-ii-bows-out-new-king-frederik-x-is-proclaimed-13048244%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fdenmarks-queen-margrethe-ii-bows-out-new-king-frederik-x-is-proclaimed-13048244%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20Yatra%202.0%20Delayed%20By%20Fog%2C%20Eclipsed%20By%20Milind%20Deora%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20son%20of%20Murli%20Deora%2C%20the%20Congress's%20fund%20collector%20and%20first%20to%20acknowledge%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20as%20'the%20real%20boss'%20way%20back%20in%201985%2C%20has%20quit%20the%20party.%20Milind%20Deora's%20post%20on%20%26quot%3BX%26quot%3B%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20that%20he%20was%20severing%20his%20family's%20%26quot%3B55-year%20connection%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20party%20eclipsed%20the%20launch%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20Yatra%202.0.%20It%20brought%20to%20the%20fore%20the%20fragility%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20and%20the%20vulnerability%20of%20Congress%20as%20it%20faces%20pushy%20alliance%20partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20portrayed%20the%20dilemma%20of%20loyal%20party%20workers%20struggling%20with%20the%20Congress's%20dithering%20versus%20the%20BJP's%20assertiveness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%20the%20Congress's%20bid%20to%20bring%20together%20the%2028-party%20alliance%20by%20organising%20a%20virtual%20conclave%20resulted%20in%2018%20skipping%20the%20Zoom%20call%2C%20including%20key%20players%20like%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Uddhav).%20The%20consensus%20of%20the%2010%20remaining%20participants%20--%20Congress%2C%20DMK%2C%20Janata%20Dal%20United%20(JDU)%2C%20AAP%2C%20CPI%2C%20CPI%20(M)%2C%20NCP%20(Sharad%20Pawar)%2C%20JMM%20and%20J%26amp%3BK%20National%20Conference%20-revolved%20around%20declaring%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20as%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20bloc%20-%20a%20suggestion%20that%20had%20emanated%20from%20the%20Trinamool%20and%20AAP%20last%20month%2C%20and%20which%20the%20Congress%20Working%20Committee%20had%20chosen%20to%20ignore%2C%20preferring%20to%20keep%20the%20focus%20on%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20as%20the%20party's%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20INDIA%20alliance's%20seat-sharing%20talks%20have%20crossed%20the%20mid-January%20deadline.%20A%20decision%20to%20set%20up%20a%20permanent%20secretariat%2C%20taken%20at%20the%20Mumbai%20conclave%20in%20September%2C%20seems%20to%20have%20evaporated.%20With%20Nitish%20Kumar%20chagrined%20by%20moves%20to%20sidestep%20him%2C%20the%20question%20of%20the%20helmsmanship%20of%20the%20Opposition%20alliance%20is%2C%20for%20now%2C%20lost%20in%20the%20Ether.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fbotisrmo_rahul-gandhi-manipur_625x300_14_January_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20corollary%20of%20the%20seat-sharing%20exercise%20has%20been%20the%20departure%20of%20Milind%20Deora%2C%20who%20doubted%20if%20his%20claim%20on%20the%20South%20Mumbai%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20would%20be%20honoured%20in%20the%20milieu%20of%20the%20anti-Modi%20alliance.%20Similar%20dilemmas%20may%20emerge%20across%20the%20country%2C%20especially%20in%20Punjab%2C%20if%20the%20Congress's%20present%20approach%20of%20'accommodation'%20persists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELow%20visibility%20due%20to%20dense%20fog%20engulfed%20the%20Delhi%20airport%20on%20Makar%20Sankranti%20morning.%20This%20delayed%20the%20departure%20of%20a%20special%20Indigo%20airlines%20flight%20that%20was%20to%20ferry%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20his%20band%20of%20loyalists%20to%20Imphal%20to%20kick-start%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra.%20As%20Congress%20leaders%20waited%20for%20take-off%2C%20news%20came%20from%20Mumbai%20that%20Milind%20Deora%2C%20who%20was%20once%20part%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20%26quot%3BG-7%26quot%3B%20core%20team%20comprising%2C%20apart%20from%20him%2C%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%2C%20Jitin%20Prasada%2C%20R.P.N.Singh%2C%20Ashok%20Tanwar%2C%20Sachin%20Pilot%20and%20Deepender%20Hooda%2C%20had%20decided%20to%20jump%20ship%20and%20climb%20aboard%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20led%20by%20Eknath%20Shinde.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20weather-induced%20poor%20visibility%20had%20delayed%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20Yatra%202.0%2C%20the%20party's%20myopia%20and%20inertia%20had%20been%20exposed%20again%20with%20yet%20another%20exit.%20Sachin%20Pilot%20and%20Deepender%20Hooda%20along%20with%20Gaurav%20Gogoi%20are%20the%20young%20crusaders%20by%20Rahul's%20side%20now.%20Scindia%20left%20in%20March%202020%20to%20join%20the%20BJP%2C%20followed%20by%20Tanwar%2C%20Prasada%20and%20Singh.%20Scindia%20is%20an%20important%20Union%20Minister%20who%20received%20accolades%20from%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20November%20during%20a%20function%20at%20Gwalior.%20During%20the%20opening%20of%20the%20Ayodhya%20airport%20earlier%20this%20month%20and%20during%20the%20inauguration%20of%20Atal%20Setu%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20the%20strobe%20lights%20were%20on%20Scindia%2C%20who%20is%20perhaps%20being%20promoted%20as%20a%20future%20face%20by%20the%20BJP%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJitin%20Prasada%20is%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20PWD%20minister%2C%20tasked%20with%20infrastructure%20development%2C%20which%20is%20Modi's%20leitmotif.%20Another%20former%20Congressman%2C%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20of%20Assam%2C%20has%20not%20only%20emerged%20as%20the%20party's%20face%20in%20the%20northeast%20but%20was%20also%20given%20a%20prime%20slot%20during%20the%20last%20BJP%20national%20executive%20meeting%20held%20in%20Hyderabad.%20Former%20Congressmen%20are%20being%20assigned%20key%20roles%20in%20the%20BJP%20and%20that%20is%20perhaps%20playing%20on%20the%20minds%20of%20political%20workers%20who%20are%20fed%20up%20with%20inertia%20in%20the%20Grand%20Old%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fvdagv3b8_rahul-gandhi_625x300_28_December_23.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20glass%20ceiling%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20and%20perhaps%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%2C%20in%20the%20Congress%2C%20creates%20a%20limitation%20for%20party%20workers.%20It%20is%20a%20similar%20case%20in%20family-dominated%20regional%20parties%20where%20either%20children%20of%20leaders%20or%20their%20nephews%20enjoy%20the%20upper%20hand.%20Such%20nepotism%20is%20missing%20in%20the%20BJP%2C%20as%20evidenced%20from%20recent%20chief%20ministerial%20choices%20and%20other%20appointments%20at%20the%20Centre%20and%20states.%20(The%20word%20'nepotism'%20has%20its%20roots%20in%20Latin%20in%20'nephew'.%20Translated%20in%20Hindi%2C%20it%20is%20%3Cem%3Ebhai-bhatijawaad%3C%2Fem%3E.)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20the%20young%20leaders%2C%20seasoned%20veterans%20like%20Amarinder%20Singh%20and%20Sunil%20Jakhar%20have%20left%20the%20Congress%20in%20Punjab.%20Legal%20eagle%20Kapil%20Sibal%20has%20quit.%20Ghulam%20Nabi%20Azad%2C%20who%20was%20the%20fulcrum%20of%20Sanjay%20Gandhi's%20Congress%20revival%20brigade%20in%201980%20has%20formed%20his%20own%20party%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20In%20Assam%2C%20former%20state%20Chief%20Bhubaneswar%20Kalita%20is%20now%20in%20the%20BJP.%20The%20recent%20Cachar%20regional%20council%20polls%20have%20shown%20the%20irrelevance%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%20Assam's%20discourse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20spokesman%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20reacted%20to%20Sunday's%20development%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BOne%20Milind%20Deora%20goes%20away%20but%20lakhs%20of%20Milinds%20remain%26quot%3B%2C%20while%20alleging%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bmahurat%26quot%3B%20(auspicious%20time)%20of%20Milind's%20departure%20had%20been%20determined%20by%20%26quot%3Bthe%20Guru%20of%20headline%20management%20sitting%20in%20Lok%20Kalyan%20Marg%26quot%3B%2C%20hinting%20at%20Narendra%20Modi.%20In%20contrast%2C%20Salman%20Khurshid%2C%20who%20was%20photographed%20seated%20next%20to%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20on%20the%20flight%20to%20Imphal%2C%20made%20a%20subdued%20comment%2C%20regretting%20that%20a%20%26quot%3Bfriend%20and%20colleague%26quot%3B%20had%20left.%20With%20advisors%20like%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20having%20their%20way%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20abrasiveness%20and%20inaccessibility%20may%20see%20more%20Milinds%20emerge%20in%20the%20coming%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMurli%20Deora%20headed%20the%20Mumbai%20unit%20of%20the%20Congress%20for%2022%20years%20(1981-2003).%20He%20began%20as%20a%20municipal%20councillor%20in%201968%20and%20went%20on%20to%20be%20a%20Union%20Minister.%20He%20came%20to%20the%20fore%20in%20Congress%20politics%20at%20a%20time%20when%20former%20party%20strongman%2C%20barrister%20Rajni%20Patel%2C%20joined%20the%20Congress%20faction%20opposed%20to%20Indira%20Gandhi%20in%201978.%20Sharad%20Pawar%20was%20then%20heading%20his%20own%20party%2C%20the%20Samanantar%20Congress%2C%20and%20running%20a%20government%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20Janata%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20were%20also%20the%20days%20when%20important%20Marwari%20businessmen%2C%20under%20the%20influence%20of%20Indian%20Express%20proprietor%20Ram%20Nath%20Goenka%2C%20were%20opposed%20to%20Indira%20Gandhi.%20Murli%20Deora%2C%20a%20Marwari%2C%20negotiated%20the%20labyrinth%20of%20India's%20financial%20capital%20and%20held%20aloft%20the%20Congress%20flag%20under%20challenging%20circumstances.%20In%201977%20he%20became%20the%20Mayor%20of%20Bombay%20(as%20Mumbai%20was%20then%20known)%20with%20the%20support%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena.%20Milind's%20migration%20from%20the%20Congress%20to%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20Sena%20may%20be%20viewed%20in%20this%20perspective.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201985%2C%20during%20the%20launch%20of%20an%20ambulance%20service%20in%20Bombay%2C%20Murli%20Deora%20had%20requested%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20to%20do%20the%20honours%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%2C%20which%20she%20did%2C%20reluctantly.%20On%20that%20occasion%2C%20Deora%20Senior's%20comment%20to%20the%20then%20Prime%20Minister%20that%20he%20(Rajiv%20Gandhi)%20was%20like%20the%20Duke%20of%20Edinburgh%20while%20Sonia%20'was%20the%20real%20boss'%20had%20gone%20viral.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E47-year-old%20Milind%20Deora%20snapping%20his%20family's%20%26quot%3B55-year-old%26quot%3B%20filial%20ties%20with%20the%20Congress%20ought%20to%20make%20the%20Grand%20Old%20Party%20sit%20up%20and%20ponder.%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20swatted%20away%20the%20exit%20notwithstanding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Shubhabrata%20Bhattacharya%20is%20a%20retired%20Editor%20and%20a%20public%20affairs%20commentator)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705241040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F87ei96p8_milind-deora_650x400_14_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Frahul-gandhis-yatra-2-0-delayed-by-fog-eclipsed-by-milind-deora-4862072%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20son%20of%20Murli%20Deora%2C%20the%20Congress's%20fund%20collector%20and%20first%20to%20acknowledge%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20as%20'the%20real%20boss'%20way%20back%20in%201985%2C%20has%20quit%20the%20party.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Frahul-gandhis-yatra-2-0-delayed-by-fog-eclipsed-by-milind-deora-4862072%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Frahul-gandhis-yatra-2-0-delayed-by-fog-eclipsed-by-milind-deora-4862072%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Frahul-gandhis-yatra-2-0-delayed-by-fog-eclipsed-by-milind-deora-4862072%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BDead%20End%2C%20Will%20Be%20Harshly%20Punished%26quot%3B%3A%20China's%20Post-Poll%20Warning%20To%20Taiwan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EChina's%20top%20diplomat%20warned%20Sunday%20that%20any%20steps%20towards%20Taiwan's%20independence%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bharshly%20punished%26quot%3B%20after%20the%20self-ruled%20island%20defied%20Beijing's%20warnings%20and%20chose%20pro-sovereignty%20candidate%20Lai%20Ching-te%20as%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVoters%20on%20the%20island%20spurned%20Beijing's%20repeated%20calls%20not%20to%20vote%20for%20Lai%2C%20delivering%20a%20comfortable%20victory%20for%20a%20man%20China's%20ruling%20Communist%20Party%20sees%20as%20a%20dangerous%20separatist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeijing%2C%20which%20claims%20Taiwan%20as%20its%20territory%20and%20has%20never%20renounced%20force%20to%20bring%20it%20under%20its%20control%2C%20responded%20to%20Lai's%20victory%20by%20saying%20it%20would%20not%20change%20the%20%26quot%3Binevitable%20trend%20of%20China's%20reunification%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20anyone%20on%20the%20island%20of%20Taiwan%20thinks%20of%20going%20for%20independence%2C%20they%20will%20be%20trying%20to%20split%20apart%20China's%20territory%2C%20and%20will%20certainly%20be%20harshly%20punished%20by%20both%20history%20and%20the%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20Wang%20Yi%20said%20in%20a%20joint%20press%20conference%20with%20his%20Egyptian%20counterpart%20Sameh%20Shoukry%20in%20Cairo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20dead%20end%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20matter%20what%20the%20results%20of%20the%20election%20are%2C%20they%20cannot%20change%20the%20basic%20fact%20that%20there%20is%20only%20one%20China%20and%20Taiwan%20is%20a%20part%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Wang%20said%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTaiwan%20has%20never%20been%20a%20country.%20It%20wasn't%20in%20the%20past%2C%20and%20it%20certainly%20won't%20be%20in%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEfforts%20to%20that%20end%2C%20Wang%20warned%2C%20%26quot%3Bseriously%20threatens%20the%20well-being%20of%20Taiwan%20compatriots%2C%20seriously%20harms%20the%20fundamental%20interests%20of%20the%20Chinese%20nation%2C%20and%20seriously%20jeopardises%20peace%20and%20stability%20in%20the%20Taiwan%20Strait%20region%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705240920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Ff9n2pm_china-taiwan_120x90_14_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchina-warning-taiwan-after-presidential-polls-dead-end-will-be-harshly-punished-4862066%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22China's%20top%20diplomat%20warned%20Sunday%20that%20any%20steps%20towards%20Taiwan's%20independence%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bharshly%20punished%26quot%3B%20after%20the%20self-ruled%20island%20defied%20Beijing's%20warnings%20and%20chose%20pro-sovereignty%20candidate%20Lai%20Ching-te%20as%20president.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchina-warning-taiwan-after-presidential-polls-dead-end-will-be-harshly-punished-4862066%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchina-warning-taiwan-after-presidential-polls-dead-end-will-be-harshly-punished-4862066%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchina-warning-taiwan-after-presidential-polls-dead-end-will-be-harshly-punished-4862066%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'We%20the%20People'%3A%20A%20Call%20to%20Remember%20What%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20Stands%20For%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F20123532%2FIMG_2186.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20a%20time%20when%20the%20country%20is%20overcome%20with%20mass%20hysteria%20about%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20at%20the%20very%20site%20where%20once%20the%20majestic%20Babri%20Masjid%20stood%2C%20we%20should%20recollect%20the%20long%20road%20we%20have%20travelled%20from%20the%20onset%20of%20the%20freedom%20struggle%20and%20commitment%20to%20a%20multi-faith%20India%20to%20the%20rapid%20slide%20to%20majoritarianism.%20It%20is%20time%20to%20reflect%20on%20the%20descent%20from%20secularism%20to%20a%20muscular%20Hinduism%20that%20casts%20a%20pall%20of%20fear%20over%20democratic%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20tragedy%20is%20that%20we%20came%20from%20a%20good%20place.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20May%201%2C%201947%2C%20Mahavir%20Tyagi%2C%20the%20Congress%20member%20from%20the%20United%20Provinces%2C%20suggested%20in%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20that%20consideration%20of%20minority%20rights%20should%20be%20postponed.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20there%20is%20to%20be%20a%20partition%2C%20we%20must%20know%20what%20is%20happening%20to%20the%20minorities%20on%20the%20other%20side%2C%20in%20the%20other%20units%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20Dr.%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%20replied%20resolutely%20that%20rights%20of%20minorities%20are%20absolute%20rights%2C%20they%20should%20not%20be%20held%20hostage%20to%20the%20policies%20of%20another%20country%20on%20its%20minorities.%20%E2%80%9CI%20think%20that%20the%20rights%20which%20are%20indicated%20in%20clause%2018%20are%20rights%20which%20every%20minority%20irrespective%20of%20any%20other%20consideration%20is%20entitled%20to.%E2%80%9D%20This%20was%20the%20ethos%20that%20India%20began%20its%20postcolonial%20life%20with.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20should%20recollect%20that%20after%20the%20massive%20communal%20riot%20in%20Kanpur%20in%201931%2C%20the%20Congress%20drafted%20the%20Karachi%20Resolution%20on%20Fundamental%20Rights.%20The%20Declaration%20emphasised%20the%20right%20of%20every%20citizen%20to%20profess%2C%20and%20practice%20her%20religion.%20Later%20that%20year%2C%20on%20March%2031%2C%20Gandhi%2C%20moving%20the%20resolution%20on%20fundamental%20rights%20in%20the%20open%20session%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%20Karachi%2C%20spoke%20on%20the%20issue.%20Though%20Islamic%20and%20Aryan%20cultures%20are%20not%20mutually%20exclusive%20he%20said%2C%20we%20must%20recognise%20that%20Muslims%20look%20upon%20Islamic%20culture%20as%20distinctive%20from%20Aryan.%20Let%20us%20therefore%20cultivate%20tolerance.%20Religious%20neutrality%20is%20an%20important%20provision.%20Swaraj%20will%20favour%20Hinduism%20no%20more%20than%20Islam%2C%20nor%20Islam%20more%20than%20Hinduism.%20Let%20us%20from%20now%20on%2C%20he%20concluded%2C%20adopt%20the%20principle%20of%20state%20neutrality%20in%20our%20daily%20affairs.%20Gandhi%20knew%20that%20independence%20would%20bring%20formidable%20problems.%20These%20problems%20had%20to%20be%20resolved%20principally%2C%20not%20by%20the%20brute%20show%20of%20power.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fprotest-at-the-parliament-should-be-seen-as-fearlessness-not-terror%5C%22%3EProtest%20at%20the%20Parliament%20Should%20Be%20Seen%20as%20Fearlessness%2C%20Not%20Terror%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDemocratic%20India%20contributed%20to%20the%20making%20of%20an%20independent%20and%20secular%20India.%20A%20group%20of%20poets%2C%20who%20later%20coalesced%20into%20the%20Progressive%20Writers%20Association%20in%201936%2C%20wrote%20amazing%20lyrics%20to%20inspire%20the%20freedom%20struggle.%20Today%20the%20country%20is%20polarised%20between%20Hindi%20and%20Urdu.%20We%20forget%20that%20Maulana%20Hasrat%20Mohani%20(1875-1951)%20coined%20the%20phrase%20%E2%80%98Inquilab%20Zindabad%E2%80%99.%20This%20became%20the%20rallying%20cry%20of%20the%20freedom%20struggle%3B%20the%20anthem%20of%20revolutionaries.%20He%20demanded%20%3Cem%3EAzaadi%20e%20Kaamil%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20complete%20independence%20in%201921%3A%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3ERasm%20e%20jafa%20kaamyab%20dekhiye%20kab%20tak%20rahe%3C%2Fem%3E%2F%3Cem%3EHubb%20e%20watan%20mast%20e%20khwab%20kab%20tak%20rahe%2FDaulat%20e%20Hindustan%20qabzah%20aghyar%20mein%2F%20Be%20adad%20O%20behisab%20dekhiye%20kab%20tak%20rahe%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Let%20us%20see%20how%20long%20we%20are%20oppressed%2C%20how%20long%20freedom%20remains%20but%20a%20dream%2C%20and%20how%20long%20the%20British%20plunder%20India%E2%80%99s%20riches).%20When%20Bhagat%20Singh%2C%20Raj%20Guru%2C%20and%20Sukhdev%20marched%20to%20the%20gallows%20they%20raised%20the%20slogan%20of%20Inquilab%20Zindabad.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20revolutionaries%20were%20inspired%20by%20Chandrashekar%20Azad%E2%80%99s%20(1906-1931)%20poem%3A%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EDushmanon%20ki%20goliyan%20ka%20hum%20samna%20karenge%2FAzad%20hi%20rahe%20hai%2C%20azaad%20hi%20rahenge%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fem%3E(We%20will%20face%20the%20bullets%20of%20the%20enemy%2C%20we%20have%20been%20free%20and%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20free)%2C%20they%20were%20equally%20motivated%20by%20the%20poet%20of%20revolution%20Josh%20Malihabadi%20(1894-1982)%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Emera%20naara%2C%20inquilab%20o%20inquilab%20o%20inquilab%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20(my%20slogan%20is%20revolution).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHow%20do%20we%20differentiate%20between%20Hindu%20and%20Muslim%20poets%3F%20Both%20loved%20freedom%20and%20both%20wrote%20such%20amazing%20poetry%20to%20capture%20political%20resistance%20that%20in%20the%20process%20they%20transformed%20literature%20and%20poetry.%20Sajjad%20Zaheer%2C%20a%20progressive%20poet%2C%20wrote%20in%20his%20autobiography%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EReminiscences%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20%E2%80%98sensitive%20writers%20felt%20that%20they%20could%20not%20continue%20in%20the%20old%20mode%E2%80%A6It%20was%20no%20longer%20possible%20for%20the%20writers%20to%20continue%20to%20live%20in%20ivory%20towers%20and%20remain%20unconcerned%20with%20the%20lives%20and%20thoughts%20of%20common%20people.%E2%80%99%20He%20was%20referring%20to%20the%20wave%20of%20anti-fascism%2C%20socialism%20and%20radicalisation%20of%20culture%2C%20literature%20and%20poetry%2C%20or%20social%20realism%2C%20that%20swept%20India%20in%20the%201930s.%20Literary%20figures%20extended%20the%20goals%20of%20the%20freedom%20struggle%20to%20the%20fight%20against%20injustice%20and%20patriarchy%20within%20society.%20Witness%20the%20contrast%20between%20progressive%20writers%20and%20rabid%20Muslim%20and%20Hindu%20right-wingers%20who%20remain%20stuck%20in%20notions%20of%20%E2%80%98two%20nations%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F07194357%2FIMG_2649.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22M20%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F07194357%2FIMG_2649.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F07194357%2FIMG_2649-300x120.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F07194357%2FIMG_2649-1024x410.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-671913%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBhisham%20and%20Balraj%20Sahni%2C%20Prithviraj%2C%20Raj%20and%20Shammi%20Kapoor%20and%20a%20number%20of%20stars%20including%20the%20debonair%20Dev%20Anand%2C%20as%20well%20poets-%20Jan%20Nisar%20Akhtar%2C%20Sahir%20Ludhianvi%2C%20and%20Sardar%20Jafri%20among%20others%2C%20spoke%20up%20and%20marched%20against%20communalism%2C%20poverty%20and%20social%20oppression%20in%201946%20in%20Bombay.%20The%20progressives%20taught%20us%20that%20society%20has%20to%20look%20outwards%20towards%20imperialism%2C%20but%20it%20also%20has%20to%20also%20look%20inwards%20and%20focus%20on%20the%20many%20contradictions%2C%20oppressions%2C%20and%20tyrannies%20of%20our%20own%20society.%20They%20radicalised%20the%20freedom%20struggle.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20first%20meeting%20of%20the%20PWA%2C%20Munshi%20Premchand%20gave%20the%20inaugural%20address%20in%20chaste%20Urdu.%20He%20told%20the%20audience%20that%20good%20literature%20can%20only%20be%20founded%20on%20truth%2C%20beauty%2C%20freedom%20and%20humanity.%20It%20has%20to%20reject%20all%20that%20inhibits%20human%20freedom%20and%20creativity%2C%20such%20as%20orthodoxy%20and%20obscurantism.%20%E2%80%98Literature%20is%20the%20outward%20form%20of%20the%20artist%E2%80%99s%20spiritual%20balance%2C%20and%20what%20harmony%20creates%20is%20never%20subversive.%20It%20nurtures%20in%20us%20the%20qualities%20of%20loyalty%2C%20sincerity%2C%20sympathy%2C%20justice%20and%20egalitarianism.%20Where%20these%20qualities%20exist%2C%20there%20is%20stability%20and%20life.%20Where%20they%20are%20wanting%2C%20there%20is%20division%2C%20selfishness%2C%20hatred%2C%20enmity%2C%20and%20death%E2%80%A6Literature%20makes%20our%20life%20natural%20and%20free%E2%80%A6it%20civilises%20the%20self.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20independence%2C%20India%20inherited%20a%20fractured%20land%20and%20a%20divided%20people.%20Partition%20was%20the%20cost%20the%20country%20paid%20for%20independence.%20A%20number%20of%20progressive%20poets%20voiced%20their%20opposition%20to%20Partition%2C%20but%20their%20hearts%20were%20heavy.%20History%2C%20after%20the%20first%20world%20war%2C%20had%20once%20again%20borne%20witness%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20nation%20had%20taken%20precedence%20over%20solidarity.%20Ahmad%20Faraz%2C%20a%20poet%20who%20had%20opted%20for%20Pakistan%2C%20wrote%20in%20despair%3A%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EAb%20kis%20ka%20jashn%20manaate%20ho%2FUs%20desh%20ka%20jo%20taqseem%20hua%2FUs%20desh%20ka%20geet%20sunaate%20ho%2FJo%20toot%20ke%20hi%20tasleem%20hua%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%5BWhat%20are%20you%20celebrating%2C%20a%20country%20which%20was%20divided%20to%20create%20Pakistan%3F%5D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpangs-of-unemployment-why-indias-youth-is-turning-to-bhagat-singh%5C%22%3EPangs%20of%20Unemployment%3A%20Why%20India%E2%80%99s%20Youth%20is%20Turning%20to%20Bhagat%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPartition%20and%20independence%20were%20the%20twin%20faces%20of%20August%201947%20in%20India.%20The%20miracle%20is%20that%20a%20democratic%20constitution%20was%20written%20amidst%20the%20debris%20of%20destroyed%20homes%2C%20work%20places%20and%20places%20of%20worship.%20It%20was%20democratic%20despite%20massacres%20and%20frayed%20hopes%20that%20independence%20would%20herald%20a%20new%20era.%20The%20task%20the%20constitution%20makers%20had%20on%20their%20hands%20was%20a%20stupendous%20one.%20Indians%20spoke%20different%20languages%2C%20practiced%20distinctive%20rituals%2C%20possessed%20unique%20world%20views%2C%20and%20had%20diverse%20expectations%20of%20politics.%20A%20newly%20independent%20India%20strained%20at%20the%20seams%20with%20diversity%20and%20difference%2C%20both%20of%20which%20can%20prove%20troublesome%20categories.%20People%20were%20strangers%20to%20each%20other.%20And%20in%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20democracy%20was%20a%20stranger%20to%20them.%20Independence%20had%20come%20along%20with%20bloodshed%20and%20massacres%2C%20social%20hierarchies%20were%20left%20intact%2C%20elites%20continued%20to%20hold%20themselves%20above%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20people%2C%20and%20discrimination%20on%20grounds%20of%20religion%20and%20caste%20ran%20rife.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnce%20again%20progressive%20poets%2C%20realising%20their%20responsibility%20to%20create%20a%20harmonious%20India%2C%20wrote%20inspiring%20lyrics%20that%20transcended%20religious%20boundaries%20to%20focus%20on%20commonalities.%20In%201960%2C%20in%20the%20famous%20film%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBarsaat%20Ki%20Raat%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20directed%20by%20P.L%20Santoshi%2C%20Sahir%20Ludhianvi%20wrote%20the%20lyrics%20of%20a%20%3Cem%3Equawali%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98yeh%20ishq%20ishq%20hai%20ishq%20ishq%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20high%20point%20of%20the%20lyric%20were%20the%20lines%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EIshaq%20azaad%20hai%20Hindu%20na%20Musalman%20hai%20Ishq%2F%20aap%20hi%20dharam%20hai%20and%20aap%20hi%20imaan%20hai%20Ishq%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Love%20is%20free%2C%20neither%20Hindu%20nor%20Muslim%2C%20it%20is%20in%20itself%20dharma%20and%20belief).%20And%20for%20a%201961%20film%2C%20B.R%20Chopra%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDharamputr%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%2C%20Sahir%20wrote%3A%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EKaabe%20mein%20rahon%20ya%20kashi%20mein%2C%20nisbat%20to%20usiki%20baat%20se%20hai%2C%20tum%20ram%20kaho%2C%20yah%20Rahim%20kaho%2C%20maqsad%20to%20usiki%20zaat%20se%20hai%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Whether%20you%20live%20in%20Kaaba%20or%20Kashi%20you%20are%20concerned%20with%20one%20God%2C%20whether%20you%20call%20him%20Ram%20or%20Rahim).%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhere%20does%20Bollywood%20stand%20today%20on%20majoritarianism%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2F14140600%2F142282.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2F14140600%2F142282.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2F14140600%2F142282-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2F14140600%2F142282-1024x768.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330200%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPhoto%3A%20Instagram%2Fkaranjohar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20constitution%20as%20a%20social%20contract%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20constitution%20is%20a%20social%20contract%20that%20establishes%20a%20relationship%20between%20citizens%20and%20the%20state.%20It%20also%20establishes%20a%20relationship%20between%20citizens.%20A%20people%20who%20had%20been%20divided%20along%20the%20lines%20of%20politicised%20religion%20had%20to%20accept%20each%20other%20as%20members%20of%20a%20democratic%20political%20community%20constituted%20by%20the%20constitution.%20They%20were%20given%20an%20alternative%20to%20living%20in%20claustrophobic%20caste%20or%20religious%20communities%2C%20to%20know%20what%20cosmopolitanism%2C%20solidarity%20and%20friendship%20meant.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20was%20introduced%20to%20new%20norms%20enshrined%20in%20the%20preamble%20of%20the%20constitution%20and%2C%20above%20all%2C%20to%20the%20recognition%20of%20the%20importance%20of%20%E2%80%98we%20the%20people%E2%80%99%20i.e.%20popular%20sovereignty.%20We%20now%20owed%20obligations%20not%20only%20to%20the%20people%20we%20had%20elected%20into%20power%2C%20but%20also%20obligations%20to%20each%20other%20as%20fellow%20citizens.%20Thus%2C%20a%20political%20community%20based%20on%20fidelity%20to%20the%20constitution%20was%20born%20which%2C%20despite%20a%20rocky%20biography%20in%20the%20years%20since%20independence%2C%20has%20been%20consolidated%20through%20political%20action%20and%20through%20the%20development%20of%20solidarity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20foundations%20of%20this%20community%20had%20been%20laid%20during%20the%20freedom%20struggle%20by%20leaders%2C%20cadres%2C%20literature%20and%20progressive%20writers%20and%20poets.%20Poet%20Brij%20Narain%20Chakbast%20(1882-1926)%20spoke%20of%20the%20ability%20of%20a%20subject%20people%20to%20rise%20in%20unity%20against%20the%20power%20of%20the%20colonial%20state%3A%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EYeh%20Khaak%20e%20Hind%20se%20paide%20hain%20josh%20ke%20aasar%2FHimalaya%20se%20uthe%20jaise%20abr-e-daryabaar.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20The%20coming%20together%20of%20people%20in%20a%20massive%20struggle%20for%20independence%20could%20have%20proved%20fragile%2C%20if%20a%20democratic%20constitution%20had%20not%20built%20on%20the%20anti-colonial%20project%20to%20create%20a%20project%20of%20solidarity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2F676925%2Fthe-opium-of-nationalism%2F%5C%22%3EThe%20Opium%20of%20Nationalism%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESolidarity%20is%20built%20upon%20civic%20mindedness%2C%20and%20good%20will%20towards%20fellow%20citizens.%20Democratic%20institutions%20will%20collapse%20if%20these%20two%20attributes%20are%20overtaken%20by%20racial%20and%20religious%20intolerance.%20Democracy%20is%20not%20only%20dependent%20on%20institutions%2C%20it%20is%20dependent%20on%20the%20relationship%20between%20citizens.%20And%20whether%20they%20see%20the%20political%20community%20as%20not%20only%20meant%20for%20the%20majority%20group%20but%20also%20their%20willingness%20to%20accept%20others%20as%20equals%20and%20as%20worthy%20of%20civil%20behaviour.%20Any%20deviation%20from%20or%20violation%20of%20these%20norms%20harm%20democracy%20and%20secularism.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThough%20Congress%20leaders%20used%20the%20term%20secularism%20in%20the%20pre-independence%20period%20often%2C%20oddly%20enough%20the%20concept%20was%20never%20spelt%20out%20or%20elaborated%20as%20a%20principle%20of%20state%20policy%20in%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly.%20Nor%20was%20it%20included%20in%20the%20preamble%20until%201976%2C%20vide%20the%2042nd%20Amendment.%20Yet%2C%20commitment%20to%20secularism%20was%20visible%20throughout%20the%20debates%20in%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20instance%2C%20most%20members%20agreed%20that%20the%20preamble%20should%20not%20contain%20any%20reference%20to%20God.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20October%2017%2C%201949%2C%20during%20discussions%20on%20the%20wording%20of%20the%20preamble%2C%20H.V.%20Kamath%20moved%20an%20amendment%20that%20it%20should%20begin%20with%20the%20phrase%20%E2%80%98In%20the%20name%20of%20God%E2%80%99.%20Similar%20amendments%20were%20moved%20by%20Shibban%20Lal%20Saxena%20and%20Pandit%20Mohan%20Malviya.%20Other%20members%20objected%2C%20and%20a%20majority%20of%20the%20members%20expressed%20their%20conviction%20that%20religion%20was%20a%20matter%20of%20individual%20choice%20and%20not%20the%20signpost%20of%20a%20collective.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F06100716%2FIMG_6848.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F06100716%2FIMG_6848.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F06100716%2FIMG_6848-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F06100716%2FIMG_6848-1024x683.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-661861%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPandit%20Hriday%20Nath%20Kunzru%20regretfully%20stated%20that%20a%20matter%20concerning%20our%20innermost%20and%20sacred%20feelings%20have%20been%20brought%20into%20the%20arena%20of%20discussion.%20It%20would%20have%20been%20far%20more%20consistent%20with%20our%20beliefs%20that%20we%20should%20not%20impose%20our%20feelings%20on%20others%2C%20and%20that%20the%20collective%20view%20should%20not%20have%20been%20forced%20on%20others.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20invoke%20the%20name%20of%C2%A0%20God%2C%20but%20I%20make%20bold%20to%20say%20that%20while%20we%20do%20so%2C%20we%20are%20showing%20a%20narrow%20sectarian%20spirit%2C%20which%20is%20contrary%20to%20the%20spirit%20of%20the%20Constitution.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20amendment%20moved%20by%20Mr%20Kamath%20was%20defeated.%20Members%20stressed%20on%20the%20need%20to%20curtail%20religion%20in%20the%20public%20sphere%20in%20the%20interests%20of%20nation%20building%2C%20of%20democracy%20and%20of%20rights.%20On%20November%2023%2C%201948%2C%20K.M%20Munshi%20emphasised%20that%20religion%20must%20be%20restricted%20to%20spheres%20which%20legitimately%20appertain%20to%20religion.%20The%20rest%20of%20life%20must%20be%20regulated%2C%20unified%20and%20modified%20in%20order%20to%20build%20a%20strong%20and%20consolidated%20nation.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20December%202%2C%201948%2C%20Dr%20Ambedkar%20asked%20for%20strict%20control%20over%20religion.%20Religious%20conceptions%20in%20this%20country%2C%20he%20said%2C%20are%20so%20vast%20that%20they%20cover%20every%20aspect%20of%20life%20from%20birth%20to%20death.%20We%20should%20strive%20to%20limit%20the%20definition%20of%20religion%20so%20that%20it%20does%20not%20extend%20beyond%20beliefs%20and%20rituals%20of%20ceremonies.%20In%20sum%2C%20the%20role%20of%20religion%20in%20public%20affairs%20was%20sought%20to%20be%20depoliticised%2C%20and%20religion%20privatised%2C%20so%20that%20the%20public%20sphere%20and%20state%20policy%20could%20be%20governed%20by%20secular%20or%20non-religious%20politics.%20This%20was%20the%20constitution%20that%20the%20people%20of%20India%20gave%20to%20themselves%20%E2%80%93%20a%20product%20of%20mass%20struggle%2C%20political%20compromises%2C%20idealism%20and%20commitment%20to%20every%20citizen.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20adoption%20of%20a%20constitution%20%E2%80%93%20whose%20preamble%20majorly%20reflected%20the%20demands%20of%20the%20freedom%20movement%20%E2%80%93%20realised%20dreams%20and%20longings%20that%20had%20been%20stirred%20by%20poetry%2C%20fiery%20speeches%20of%20revolution%2C%20political%20protests%20and%20by%20the%20selfless%20devotion%20of%20outstanding%20men%20and%20women%20to%20the%20country.%20The%20day%20the%20constitution%20was%20promulgated%20on%20January%2026%2C%201950%2C%20was%20a%20day%20of%20great%20joy%20and%20fulfilment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20perhaps%2C%20the%20constitution%20began%20to%20be%20taken%2C%20by%20succeeding%20generations%2C%20for%20granted%20except%20as%20a%20document%20that%20has%20been%20interpreted%20and%20reinterpreted%20by%20the%20courts.%20I%20wonder%20how%20many%20Indians%20recognise%20that%20the%20constitution%20is%20also%20political%20document.%20The%20preamble%20embodies%20the%20ideals%20of%20a%20generation%20that%20fought%20for%20independence%20for%20generations%20that%20were%20to%20follow.%20What%20else%20were%20people%20fighting%20for%20if%20they%20were%20not%20fighting%20against%20the%20might%20of%20the%20colonial%20power%20for%20independence.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EToday%2C%20we%20should%20re-discover%20that%20moment%20of%20excitement%20and%20joy%20when%20India%20got%20her%20own%20constitution.%20We%20need%20to%20rediscover%20that%20sense%20of%20pride%20that%20our%20constitution%20has%20been%20fought%20for%20by%20millions%20of%20people%2C%20for%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20constitution%20which%20embodied%20the%20commitment%20of%20the%20national%20movement%20is%20considered%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20finest%20in%20the%20world.%20There%20is%20nothing%20a%20people%20cannot%20do%20when%20they%20come%20together%20in%20a%20community%20that%20transcends%20caste%2C%20regional%20and%20religious%20affiliations.%20A%20people%20who%20unite%20in%20the%20associational%20space%20of%20the%20political%20community%20have%20great%20power.%20That%20is%20why%20so-called%20leaders%2C%20and%20political%20parties%20aspiring%20to%20power%2C%20try%20to%20divide%20people%20along%20the%20lines%20of%20religious%20affiliation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYet%2C%20the%20political%20community%2C%20relatively%20autonomous%20of%20the%20rites%20of%20procedural%20politics%2C%20and%20characterised%20by%20deliberation%20and%20dialogue%20reiterates%20a%20truth%20that%20is%20often%20overlooked%20by%20legal%20jurists.%20A%20society%20cannot%20be%20held%20together%20only%20by%20the%20dry%20bones%20of%20law.%20Unless%20people%20relate%20to%20each%20other%20with%20sympathy%20because%20they%20are%20fellow%20citizens%2C%20and%20who%20inhabit%20a%20community%20of%20fate%2C%20legal%20ties%20can%20prove%20brittle%2C%20laws%20can%20be%20subverted%2C%20corrupted%20and%20ignored.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPolitical%20communities%20should%20be%20able%20to%20reach%20out%20and%20connect%20with%20each%20other%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20poetic%20sympathy%20and%20solidarity.%20Otherwise%2C%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20live%20in%20the%20Hobbesian%20pre-political%20state%20of%20potential%20war%20against%20others.%20And%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20ask%20ourselves%2C%20did%20not%20we%20not%20learn%20anything%20from%20history%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fneera-chandhoke%5C%22%3ENeera%20Chandhoke%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20a%20professor%20of%20political%20science%20at%20Delhi%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705240906000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F20123532%2FIMG_2186.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwe-the-people-a-call-to-remember-what-the-indian-constitution-stands-for%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20constitution%20that%20the%20people%20of%20India%20gave%20to%20themselves%20was%20a%20product%20of%20mass%20struggle%2C%20political%20compromises%2C%20idealism%20and%20commitment%20to%20every%20citizen.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwe-the-people-a-call-to-remember-what-the-indian-constitution-stands-for%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BBeyond%20Human%20Control%26quot%3B%3A%20Sonu%20Sood's%20Plea%20After%20Being%20Stuck%20At%20Airport%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20dense%20fog%20blanket%20wreaking%20havoc%20on%20flight%20operations%20amid%20the%20ongoing%20winter%20season%2C%20actor%20Sonu%20Sood%20shared%20a%20scene%20of%20horrifying%20chaos%20in%20the%20waiting%20area%20of%20an%20airport.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%2C%20known%20for%20his%20goodwill%2C%20urged%20the%20stranded%20passengers%20to%20treat%20the%20crew%20of%20airlines%20with%20kindness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20the%20actor%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20weather%20Gods%20have%20their%20own%20moods%2C%20beyond%20human%20control!!%20I%20have%20been%20patiently%20waiting%20for%20the%20last%203%20hours%20at%20the%20airport.%20I%20know%20it's%20difficult%20but%20request%20everyone%20to%20be%20polite%20with%20the%20airline