sending%20lava%20flowing%20towards%20a%20fishing%20village%20that%20had%20to%20be%20evacuated%20overnight.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A710%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fvolcano-erupts-in-same-iceland-peninsula-where-lava-emerged-from-a-huge-crack-in-the-ground-in-december-13048028%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fvolcano-erupts-in-same-iceland-peninsula-where-lava-emerged-from-a-huge-crack-in-the-ground-in-december-13048028%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fvolcano-erupts-in-same-iceland-peninsula-where-lava-emerged-from-a-huge-crack-in-the-ground-in-december-13048028%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mosque%20on%20Govt's%20Demolition%20Radar%20Has%20Ties%20to%20India's%20Constituent%20Assembly%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F14123819%2FGCdO1LYa0AAmK3w.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Ecelebrating%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EAzadi%20ka%20Amrit%20Mahotsav%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehas%20a%20separate%20section%20for%20the%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eunsung%20heroes%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20freedom%20struggle%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D.%20Listed%20amongst%20these%20heroes%20is%20the%20famous%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EMaulana%20Hasrrat%20Mohani%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20Maulana%2C%20though%20initially%20elected%20on%20a%20Muslim%20League%20ticket%2C%20was%20a%20staunch%20opponent%20of%20the%20two-nation%20theory%20and%20was%20among%20those%20Muslims%20who%20decided%20to%20stay%20back%20in%20India%2C%20contributing%20significantly%20to%20the%20constitution-making%20process%20as%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20principles%20did%20not%20allow%20him%20to%20avail%20of%20any%20government%20allowances%20or%20accommodations.%20Even%20to%20attend%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%2C%20he%20would%20choose%20to%20stay%20in%20mosques%20and%20ride%20in%20a%20shared%20%3Cem%3Et%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3Eonga%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E(horse%20carriage)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20One%20such%20mosque%20was%20a%20small%20but%20old%20one%20at%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ESunehri%20Bagh%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ERoundabout%2C%20in%20close%20proximity%20to%20Raisina%20Hill.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20small%20mosque%20at%20Sunehri%20Bagh%2C%20whose%20history%20reveals%20its%20survival%20even%20against%20Edwin%20Lutyens%E2%80%99%20plan%20for%20New%20Delhi%2C%20has%20found%20itself%20in%20the%20eye%20of%20the%20storm%20over%20a%20century%20later.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20cause%20is%20a%20notice%20inviting%20suggestions%20issued%20by%20the%20New%20Delhi%20Municipal%20Corporation%20(NDMC)%20regarding%20a%20proposal%20for%20its%20removal.%20The%20proposal%2C%20as%20the%20notice%20indicates%2C%20is%20submitted%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Traffic%20Police%2C%20ostensibly%20for%20providing%20a%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Etraffic%20engineering%20proposal%20to%20ensure%20sustainable%20mobility.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20undoubtedly%20true%20that%20the%20mosque%20is%20a%20Delhi%20Waqf%20Board%20property%20and%20has%20been%20standing%20tall%20for%20centuries.%20As%20pointed%20out%20by%20numerous%20historians%2C%20it%20is%20an%20important%20heritage%20structure%20not%20only%20for%20Muslims%20but%20also%20for%20the%20democratic%20history%20of%20our%20nation.%20It%20serves%20as%20a%20reminder%20of%20one%20of%20the%20unsung%20heroes%20of%20the%20freedom%20struggle%2C%20whom%20we%20celebrate%20during%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EAzadi%20ka%20Amrit%20Mahotsav%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20However%2C%20beyond%20the%20questions%20of%20religion%20and%20the%20rights%20of%20%E2%80%98minorities%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20a%20term%20that%20was%20not%20much%20to%20the%20liking%20of%20the%20Maulana%20either%20%E2%80%94%20a%20larger%20question%20of%20equality%20and%20reasonableness%20arises.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fconstant-attempt-to-erode-medieval-architecture-heritage-historians-org-on-sunehri-bagh-mosque%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Constant%20Attempt%20to%20Erode%20Medieval%20Architecture%2C%20Heritage%E2%80%99%3A%20Historians%20Org%20on%20Sunehri%20Bagh%20Mosque%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20the%20issue%20genuinely%20pertains%20to%20traffic%20management%2C%20Lutyens%E2%80%99%20Delhi%20is%20now%20marked%20by%20an%20abundance%20of%20such%20roundabouts%2C%20leading%20to%20occasional%20traffic%20congestion%20at%20various%20points%20throughout%20the%20day%20%E2%80%93%20an%20inherent%20characteristic%20of%20any%20major%20city%20worldwide.%20A%20notable%20instance%20is%20the%20GPO%20Roundabout%2C%20hosting%20the%20renowned%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EGole%20Dak-Khana%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ewithin%2C%20and%20flanked%20by%20Gurudwara%20Bangla%20Sahib%20on%20one%20side%20and%20the%20Convent%20of%20Jesus%20and%20Mary%20on%20the%20other.%20During%20midday%2C%20on%20school%20days%2C%20this%20roundabout%20experiences%20significant%20traffic%20congestion.%20Similarly%2C%20lawyers%20returning%20from%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20their%20offices%20during%20the%20lunch%20hour%20have%20learnt%20over%20time%20that%20it%20is%20best%20to%20avoid%20the%20Mathura%20Road%20turning%20near%20the%20Delhi%20Public%20School.%20Would%20such%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Econgestion%20%E2%80%94%20undoubtedly%20more%20pronounced%20than%20at%20the%20Sunehri%20Bagh%20roundabout%20%E2%80%94%20justify%20the%20removal%20of%20historical%20structures%20and%20even%20schools%3F%20The%20unequivocal%20answer%20is%20obvious.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20nation%20governed%20by%20the%20rule%20of%20law%2C%20with%20its%20constitution%20built%20upon%20the%20founding%20principles%20of%20equality%20and%20fraternity%2C%20any%20state%20action%20is%20scrutinised%20based%20on%20the%20level%20of%20reasonability%20of%20the%20action%20with%20the%20intended%20objective.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Sunehri%20Bagh%20roundabout%20accommodates%20a%20small%20historical%20mosque%20in%20one%20section%2C%20while%20the%20remainder%20is%20largely%20occupied%20by%20the%20unsightly%20mechanical%20vents%20of%20the%20Udyog%20Bhawan%20metro%20station%20situated%20directly%20beneath%20the%20roundabout.%20The%20site%20is%20also%20surrounded%20by%20a%20cluster%20of%20government%20buildings%2C%20including%20Vayu%20Bhawan%2C%20Udyog%20Bhawan%2C%20and%20Nirman%20Bhawan.%20Moreover%2C%20at%20least%20three%20entrances%20of%20the%20Udyog%20Bhawan%20metro%20station%20encircle%20the%20roundabout%2C%20attracting%20auto-rickshaws%20and%20other%20vehicles%20parked%20nearby.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20issues%20of%20architecture%2C%20heritage%20and%20history%20may%20be%20addressed%20appropriately%20by%20the%20experts%20of%20the%20field%2C%20the%20legal%20issue%20can%20be%20stated%20as%20to%20the%20reasonableness%20of%20the%20need%20for%20removal%20of%20the%20mosque%20when%20the%20structure%20itself%20cannot%20be%20blamed%20for%20whatever%20negligible%20traffic%20the%20wide%20roads%20in%20the%20Lutyens%20area%20may%20see.%20Equally%2C%20the%20proposal%20given%20by%20the%20Traffic%20Police%20lacks%20any%20intelligible%20differentia%20for%20the%20classification%20made%20in%20seeking%20removal%20of%20one%20structure%20while%20other%20areas%20of%20Delhi%20remain%20marred%20by%20worse%20traffic%20or%20any%20reasonable%20nexus%20to%20demonstrate%20how%20%E2%80%9Csustainable%20mobility%E2%80%9D%20is%20to%20be%20obtained%20by%20removal%20of%20a%20heritage%20structure.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EComing%20back%20to%20the%20Maulana%2C%20a%20lesser%20known%20fact%20of%20his%20life%20is%20that%20apart%20from%20being%20an%20astute%20statesman%2C%20parliamentarian%20and%20one%20of%20the%20prominent%20freedom%20fighters%2C%20he%20was%20also%20an%20Urdu%20poet%20of%20considerable%20skill%20and%20charm.%20The%20famous%20ghazal%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Echupke%20chupke%20raat%20din%20aansu%20bahana%20yaad%20hai%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20immortalised%20in%20our%20memories%20in%20the%20voice%20of%20Ustad%20Ghulam%20Ali%2C%20was%20also%20his%20creation.%20While%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Echupke%20chupke%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ewould%20ring%20a%20tune%20in%20anyone%E2%80%99s%20mind%20even%20though%20they%20may%20not%20be%20aware%20of%20the%20Maulana%2C%20given%20the%20subject%20one%20cannot%20resist%20the%20temptation%20to%20quote%20one%20of%20his%20lesser%20known%20couplets%20where%20he%20said%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cv%C4%81qif%20hai%C3%B1%20%E1%B8%B3huub%20aap%20ke%20tarz-e-jaf%C4%81%20se%20ham%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eiz.h%C4%81r-e-iltif%C4%81t%20k%C4%AB%20zahmat%20na%20k%C4%ABjiye%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(Well%20aware%20I%20am%20of%20your%20tyrannies%2C%20please%20spare%20yourself%20from%20the%20trouble%20of%20stating%20the%20same).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EFuzail%20Ahmad%20Ayyubi%20is%20Advocate-on-Record%20Supreme%20court.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705219218000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F14123819%2FGCdO1LYa0AAmK3w.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmosque-on-govts-demolition-radar-has-ties-to-indias-constituent-assembly%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20small%20mosque%20at%20Sunehri%20Bagh%2C%20whose%20history%20reveals