there%20is%20no%20denying%2C%20so%20far%2C%20that%20the%20opposition%20appears%20less-than-ready%20to%20meet%20their%20formidable%20challenger.%20Of%20course%2C%20they%20have%20declared%20their%20coalition%20will%20take%20on%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20as%20one.%20The%20pro-BJP%20media%20has%20sniggered%20and%20declared%20their%20reluctance%20to%20attend%20the%20consecration%20of%20Ram%20into%20the%20new%20temple%20at%20Ayodhya%20as%20%E2%80%9Canti-Hindu%E2%80%9D%20and%20their%20coalition%20formation%20exercise%20as%20a%20non%20starter.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20coming%202024%20general%20elections%2C%20the%20Modi-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20will%20be%20challenged%20by%20the%20grand%20coalition%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%2C%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20the%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%2C%20the%20Left%20and%20several%20other%20regional%20groups.%20Their%20view%20is%20that%20coalition%20politics%20in%20India%20offers%20a%20voluntary%20response%20to%20an%20involuntary%20situation%20ever%20since%20the%2011%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ELok%20Sabha%20elections%20resulted%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20hung%20parliament.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20challenging%20a%20power%20structure%20is%20beyond%20the%20grasp%20of%20any%20single%20party%E2%80%99s%20reach%2C%20all%20parties%2C%20regional%20or%20national%2C%20must%20challenge%20it%20unitedly.%20It%20is%20not%20easy%20to%20make%20parties%20soften%20their%20ideological%20stand%20and%20step%20away%20from%20caste%20fault-lines.%20But%20history%20sometimes%20throws%20up%20an%20ideal%20catalytic%20agent%20who%20can%20make%20it%20happen.%20The%20BJP%20and%20its%20ardent%20followers%20pick%20and%20choose%20Puranic%20stories%20that%20play%20up%20the%20role%20of%20empire-builder%20kings%20as%20unifiers%2C%20playing%20down%20the%20coalition%20makers%20who%20shed%20political%20ambitions%20and%20diplomatically%20persuaded%20several%20warring%20republics%20under%20one%20umbrella.%20One%20outstanding%20example%20is%20that%20of%20Krishna.%20This%20is%20not%20the%20mischievous%20cowherd%20and%20heart-breaker%20of%20%3Cem%3Egopika%3C%2Fem%3Es%20or%20milkmaids%20in%20the%20Braj%20Bhumi%2C%20but%20the%20mature%20Krishna%20of%20Dwarika.%20Today%2C%20many%20insist%20on%20labelling%20him%20as%20Dwarikadheesh%2C%20the%20lord%20of%20Dwarika.%20But%20Krishna%20was%20never%20a%20king%20of%20Mathura%20or%20Dwarika.%20He%20was%20a%20coalition%20maker%20who%20helped%20bring%20about%20a%20union%20between%20clans%20like%20the%C2%A0%20Andhaka%20and%20the%20Vrishnis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Dwarika%20of%20Krishna%20operated%20as%20an%20oligarchy%20under%20various%20clans.%20But%20not%20before%20it%20gave%20a%20hard%20time%20to%20the%20creator%20of%20the%20coalition%20who%20had%20to%20handle%20bitter%20inner%20squabbling.%20In%20%3Cem%3EMahabharat%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20Krishna%20confides%20to%20his%20close%20confidant%20Narada%20how%20tired%20he%20is%20of%20handling%20problems%20between%20warring%20clans.%20Narada%20reminds%20him%2C%20%E2%80%98But%20you%20are%20the%20head%20of%20a%20coalition%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Sangh%20Mukhyoasi%20Keshav.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98You%20can%20not%20give%20up!%20Assert%20yourself!%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20But%20Krishna%20like%20Gandhi%20and%20Jayprakash%20Narayan%2C%20had%20no%20imperial%20ambitions%20of%20his%20own.%20He%20killed%20the%20beastly%20king%20Kamsa%20but%20crowned%20someone%20else.%20In%20fact%20Shishupal%20later%20mocked%20him%20for%20not%20wearing%20a%20crown%2C%20calling%20him%20%E2%80%98Araja%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKrishna%E2%80%99s%20coalition%20split%20when%20a%20fratricidal%20war%20became%20unavoidable.%20The%20armies%20and%20commanders%20of%20the%20coalition%20fought%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20Kauravas.%20But%20Krishna%20himself%20chose%20to%20pick%20up%20arms%20and%20instead%20drove%20Arjun%E2%80%99s%20chariot%20because%20he%20felt%20Duryodhan%20was%20a%20nascent%20dictator.%20His%20elder%20brother%20Balram%20was%20so%20enraged%20by%20the%20split%20that%20he%20too%20refused%20to%20fight.%20As%20he%20left%20with%20his%20plough%2C%20he%20accused%20Krishna%20of%20tilting%20towards%20his%20friends%20but%20Krishna%E2%80%99s%20defence%20was%20that%20in%20his%20opinion%20Duryodhana%20was%20an%20imperialist%20fuelled%20by%20pride%20and%20envy%20with%20ambitions%20of%20being%20a%20Chakravartin%20like%20Kamsa.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERight%20now%2C%20fuelled%20by%20envy%2C%20anger%20and%20casteism%2C%20the%20cycle%20of%20federal%20history%20of%20India%20seems%20to%20be%20moving%20so%20fast%20that%20one%20fears%20the%20wheels%20may%20just%20come%20off%20at%20some%20point.%20Not%20too%20long%20ago%2C%20some%20of%20the%20richest%20men%20in%20India%20appeared%20as%20discussants%20about%20India%E2%80%99s%20growing%20power%20in%20various%20widely%20beamed%20shows%20that%20are%20now%20mounted%20by%20big%20media%20houses.%20In%20India%2C%20these%20folks%20go%20up%20or%20down%20the%20%3Cem%3EForbes%3C%2Fem%3E%20list%20but%20they%20remain%20our%20big%20media%20barons%20forever.%20The%20elephant%20in%20the%20room%20today%20is%20that%20our%20lives%20and%20indeed%2C%20our%20entire%20developmental%20planning%2C%20are%20fast%20becoming%20dependent%20on%20a%20set%20of%20unelected%20billionaires%20who%20have%20also%20acquired%20most%20of%20our%20mainstream%20media.%20As%20in%20the%20USA%2C%20they%20now%20can%2C%20if%20they%20wish%2C%20swing%20elections%20and%20prevail%20upon%20chosen%20representatives%20to%20reshape%20public%20policies%20and%20laws.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20a%20writer%2C%20one%20must%20frankly%20state%20the%20absurdity%20of%20one%E2%80%99s%20position%20in%20this%20strange%20scenario.%20Autocratic%20heads%20of%20state%20are%20being%20re-elected%20in%20many%20democratic%20nations%2C%20the%20UN%20is%20withering%20visibly%20and%20the%20EU%E2%80%99s%20erstwhile%20willingness%20to%20take%20in%20immigrants%20has%20developed%20huge%20cracks.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fwhy-israels-supporters-in-the-west-are-no-friends-of-jews%5C%22%3ESome%20erstwhile%20hunted%20ethnic%20groups%2C%20having%20done%20well%2C%20have%20turned%20heartless%20ethnic%20cleansers%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20ex-bureaucrats%20and%20judges%2C%20the%20grand%20guards%20of%C2%A0%20objectivity%20and%20secularism%20are%20seen%20bowing%20to%20temple%20priests%20and%20organizing%20mega%20religious%20spectacles.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisrael-genocidal-south-africa-gaza-irish-lawyer%5C%22%3EIsrael%20Could%20Perpetrate%20More%20Genocidal%20Acts%3A%20Lawyer%20for%20South%20Africa%20at%20ICJ%20Hearings%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20here%2C%20we%2C%20the%20writers%20and%20historians%20are%20still%20attending%20literary%20festivals%20and%20writers%E2%80%99%20meets%20and%20speaking%20against%20racism%2C%20casteism%20and%20sexism.%20We%20know%20well%20how%20racially%20homogenous%20societies%20have%20not%20been%20necessarily%20happier%20or%20more%20peaceful.%20We%20also%20can%20not%20claim%20that%20democratisation%20is%20an%20easy%20process%20or%20that%20there%20are%20easy%20answers%20to%20its%20current%20problems%2C%20but%20these%20for%20heaven%E2%80%99s%20sake%2C%20are%20some%20of%20the%20darkest%20times%20we%20have%20known.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%2C%20whose%20business%20is%20the%20intimate%20lives%20of%20the%20sea%20of%20humanity%20around%20us%E2%80%A6what%20does%20the%20failure%20of%20multiculturalism%20herald%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20we%20are%20asked%20this%20by%20genuinely%20puzzled%20young%2C%20it%20implies%20that%20not%20just%20the%20politicians%20but%20human%20cultures%20too%20have%20failed%20all%20of%20us%20and%20that%20Indians%20are%20no%20longer%20capable%20of%20living%20peacefully%20together%20with%20those%20who%20follow%20different%20cultures.%20What%20the%20publicists%20for%20the%20temple%20have%20done%20is%2C%20used%20it%20as%20a%20wistful%20whimsy%20to%20drum%20up%20a%20time%20when%20all%20of%20India%20was%20Hindu%2C%20and%20spun%20it%20into%20a%20powerful%20political%20narrative.%20And%20from%20billionaires%20doing%20pilgrimage%20rounds%20to%20Bollywood%20biggies%20with%20%3Cem%3Erudrakshmala%3C%2Fem%3Es%20and%20%3Cem%3Etilak%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20everyone%20is%20using%20this%20reborn%20Hinduism%20to%20get%20what%20they%20want.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20at%20the%20UN%20they%20refuse%20to%20see%20how%20the%20world%20now%20is%20ruled%20by%20digital%20capital%20armed%20with%20AI.%20It%20no%20longer%20accepts%20old%20international%20borders%20or%20human%20rights.%20It%20is%20out%20to%20eradicate%20vast%20money-guzzling%20human%20labour%2C%20large%20offices%20with%20coffee%20machines%20and%20gossip%20corners%2C%20or%20even%20the%20human%20need%20for%20sleep.%20Real%20progress%20%E2%80%93%20when%20it%20comes%20%E2%80%93%20will%20be%20incremental%20at%20best.%20The%20dream%20of%20time%20travel%20into%20Ram%20Rajya%20on%20the%20wings%20of%20a%20temple%2C%20I%20am%20sorry%20dears%2C%20is%20just%20that%20%E2%80%93%20a%20dream.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3ESaakhi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20is%20a%20Sunday%20column%20from%20Mrinal%20Pande%2C%20in%20which%20she%20writes%20of%20what%20she%20sees%20and%20also%20participates%20in.%20That%20has%20been%20her%20burden%20to%20bear%20ever%20since%20she%20embarked%20on%20a%20life%20as%20a%20journalist%2C%20writer%2C%20editor%2C%20author%20and%20as%20chairperson%20of%20Prasar%20Bharti.%20Her%20journey%20of%20being%20a%20witness-participant%20continues.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22