3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Sharply%20escalating%20the%20rhetoric%20with%20an%20eye%20towards%20India%2C%20Maldives%20President%20Mohamed%20Muizzu%20said%20that%20the%20archipelago%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20was%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20in%20backyard%20of%20any%20particular%20country%E2%80%9D%20and%20was%20actively%20working%20to%20reduce%20dependence%20on%20procuring%20essential%20commodities%20from%20a%20single%20nation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20strong%20words%20by%20the%20Maldivian%20President%20came%20while%20addressing%20reporters%20on%20his%20return%20to%20the%20Maldives%20from%20a%20five-day%20state%20visit%20to%20China%20on%20Saturday%2C%20January%2014.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20in%20the%20first%20major%20election%20into%20Muizzu%E2%80%99s%20presidency%2C%20the%20ruling%20coalition%20lost%20the%20capital%20city%20Mal%C3%A9%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.sun.mv%2F87039%5C%22%3Em%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.sun.mv%2F87039%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eayoral%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20elections%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20the%20opposition%2C%20Maldivian%20Democratic%20Party.%20This%20election%20was%20necessitated%20by%20Muizzu%E2%80%99s%20resignation%20as%20Mal%C3%A9%20mayor%20following%20his%20victory%20in%20last%20November%E2%80%99s%20presidential%20election.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20weekend%2C%20the%20Maldivian%20government%20had%20%E2%80%9Csuspended%E2%80%9D%20three%20deputy%20ministers%20for%20making%20disparaging%20remarks%20against%20the%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20after%20his%20visit%20to%20the%20Lakshadweep%20islands.%20Following%20the%20tweets%2C%20several%20Indian%20celebrities%20started%20to%20post%20together%20that%20they%20will%20boycott%20the%20Maldives%20as%20a%20tourist%20destination.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20government%20had%20summoned%20the%20Maldivian%20ambassador%20to%20South%20Block%20last%20Monday.%20On%20the%20same%2C%20the%20Indian%20envoy%20went%20to%20the%20Maldivian%20foreign%20ministry%20for%20what%20was%20later%20described%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpre-arranged%E2%80%9D%20meeting.%20It%20had%20seemed%20that%20the%20two%20sides%20were%20trying%20to%20bring%20down%20the%20temperature%20as%20neither%20side%20provided%20any%20further%20details.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%2C%20Muizzu%20on%20return%20to%20Maldives%20seemed%20to%20have%20jumped%20into%20the%20fray.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Licence%20to%20bully%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20in%20the%20backyard%20of%20any%20particular%20country.%20We%20are%20an%20independent%20and%20sovereign%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20in%20answer%20to%20a%20question%20at%20a%20media%20conference%20at%20the%20Velana%20International%20Airport.%20He%20asserted%20that%20China%20respected%20Maldives%E2%80%99%20territorial%20integrity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Maldivian%20President%20stated%20that%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20is%20not%20the%20exclusive%20domain%20of%20any%20specific%20nation%20and%20noted%20that%20the%20Maldives%20holds%20a%20significant%20stake%20in%20the%20vast%20expanse%20of%20this%20ocean.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20though%20our%20islands%20are%20small%2C%20we%20are%20a%20huge%20country%20with%20a%20very%20large%20exclusive%20economic%20zone%20of%20nine%20lakh%20square%20kilometres.%20Maldives%20is%20one%20country%20that%20holds%20the%20largest%20proportion%20of%20this%20ocean.%20This%20ocean%20is%20not%20the%20property%20of%20a%20specific%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMuizzu%20even%20took%20a%20swipe%20at%20the%20earlier%20President%20Mohamed%20Solih%20for%20having%20a%20close%20relation%20with%20India%2C%20but%20without%20mentioning%20New%20Delhi%20directly.%20He%20said%2C%20as%20per%20the%20Maldivian%20media%2C%20that%20Solih%20had%20to%20take%20permission%20from%20a%20foreign%20government%20%E2%80%9Cto%20get%20up%20from%20one%20chair%20and%20sit%20on%20another%20chair%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMuizzu%20had%20won%20the%20presidential%20elections%20and%20stopped%20Solih%E2%80%99s%20re-election%20bid%20by%20campaigning%20on%20a%20platform%20with%20the%20slogan%20of%20%E2%80%98India%20Out%E2%80%99.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fmaldives-president-asks-india-to-withdraw-its-troops%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20second%20day%20of%20his%20presidency%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Muizzu%20had%20called%20on%20India%20to%20remove%20Indian%20security%20personnel%20stationed%20in%20Maldives.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20might%20be%20a%20small%20country%2C%20but%20that%20does%20not%20give%20you%20the%20licence%20to%20bully%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrade%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETill%20now%2C%20all%20democratically-elected%20Maldivian%20Presidents%20had%20chosen%20India%20as%20their%20first%20foreign%20trip.%20Muizzu%20chose%20to%20go%20to%20Turkey%20and%20then%20UAE%20last%20year%2C%20following%20which%20he%20travelled%20to%20China%20for%20his%20first%20state%20visit.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Maldivian%20President%20pledged%20to%20diminish%20Maldives%E2%80%99%20reliance%20on%20India%20across%20multiple%20sectors.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMaldives%20primarily%20relies%20on%20India%20as%20its%20main%20supplier%20of%20essential%20commodities%2C%20with%20New%20Delhi%20providing%20a%20special%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcontent.dgft.gov.in%2FWebsite%2Fdgftprod%2Fae06ad43-ecbd-40b1-afff-53a2f8649e30%2FNoti%252014%2520Eng.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eannual%20quota%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20items%20such%20as%20eggs%2C%20potatoes%2C%20sugar%2C%20dal%2C%20rice%2C%20wheat%20flour%2C%20stone%20aggregates%2C%20and%20river%20sand%2C%20exempt%20from%20restrictions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.sun.mv%2F87038%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20media%20reports%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Muizzu%20said%20that%20the%20government%20%E2%80%9Cwill%20hopefully%20stop%20bringing%20low-quality%20medicine%20and%20opt%20to%20bring%20medicine%20directly%20from%20the%20original%20manufacturer%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20hopefully%20change%20it%20to%20import%20medicine%20from%20Europe%20and%20the%20US%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMuizzu%20also%20asserted%20that%20he%20will%20diversify%20sources%20for%20essential%20commodities%20for%20rice-sugar%20and%20flour.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20announced%20that%20his%20government%20successfully%20struck%20a%20deal%20with%20Turkey%20and%20has%20initiated%20the%20order%20for%20the%20inaugural%20shipment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20haven%E2%80%99t%20just%20arranged%20for%20the%20supply.%20In%20a%20first%2C%20this%20Ramadan%2C%20the%20government%20will%20donate%20a%2010-kg%20rice%20bag%20and%20a%2010-kg%20flour%20bag%20to%20each%20and%20every%20household%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705208803000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F14103358%2FGDvFFVLbgAAmZK2.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fmaldives-muizzu-china-india-backyard-bully%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Muizzu%20also%20asserted%20that%20he%20will%20diversify%20sources%20for%20essential%20commodities%20for%20rice-sugar%20and%20flour.%20So%20far%20Maldives%20has%20primarily%20relied%20on%20India%20as%20its%20main%20supplier.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A40%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fmaldives-muizzu-china-india-backyard-bully%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hold%20on%20to%20Your%20Beliefs%2C%20or%20the%20World%20Will%20Convince%20You%20You're%20the%20Crazy%20One%3A%20Anuja%20Chauhan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F13195552%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-13-at-7.54.47-PM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKozhikode%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EAfter%20the%20success%20and%20awards%20she%20got%20for%20her%20romance%20novels%2C%20advertising-professional-turned-writer%20Anuja%20Chauhan%20has%20now%20turned%20to%20detective%20fiction.%20Her%20crime-solving%20protagonist%20ACP%20Bhavani%20first%20made%20an%20appearance%20in%20%3Cem%3EClub%20You%20to%20Death%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20has%20returned%20in%20Chauhan%E2%80%99s%20most%20recent%20book%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Fast%20and%20the%20Dead%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20genre%20she%20has%20named%20%E2%80%98romcrom%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20romance%2C%20crime%20and%20comedy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%98fast%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20title%20refers%20to%20Karwa%20Chauth.%20The%20novel%20is%20based%20in%20Bangalore%E2%80%99s%20Shivajinagar%2C%20in%20one%20galli%20where%20everyone%20knows%20each%20other%20%E2%80%93%20or%20think%20they%20do%2C%20until%20a%20murder%20takes%20place%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20fast.%20The%20murdered%20man%E2%80%99s%20wife%20had%20broken%20her%20%E2%80%98KC%E2%80%99%20fast%20earlier%20that%20day%2C%20leading%20to%20talk%20from%20some%20that%20she%20caused%20his%20death%2C%20while%20others%20scoff%20at%20that%20theory%20and%20the%20superstition%20it%20involves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20like%20the%20darkness%20in%20that%20juxtaposition%20%E2%80%93%20of%20the%20man%20being%20murdered%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20fast%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chauhan%20said%20at%20the%20Kerala%20Literature%20Festival%20on%20Saturday%20(January%2013).%20Chauhan%20says%20she%20thinks%20that%20Karwa%20Chauth%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Cblind%20superstition%E2%80%9D%20that%20has%20spread%20across%20the%20country%20because%20of%20its%20portrayals%20in%20Bollywood%2C%20and%20the%20differing%20viewpoints%20on%20the%20subject%20come%20across%20from%20the%20characters%20of%20her%20book.%20%E2%80%9CI%20like%20putting%20irreverent%20dialogues%20in%20my%20characters%E2%80%99%20mouths%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20laughed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20book%20is%20very%20much%20a%20detective%20story%20set%20in%20a%20micro-locality%2C%20changes%20that%20India%20has%20seen%20over%20the%20last%20decade%20and%20more%20have%20seeped%20in.%20A%20young%2C%20successful%20Muslim%20actor%20is%20a%20suspect%2C%20and%20TV%20news%20channels%20immediately%20bay%20for%20his%20blood%20and%20run%20hashtags%20that%20call%20him%20a%20murderer.%20%E2%80%9CA%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20this%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20happened%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chauhan%20explained.%20%E2%80%9CHis%20Muslim%20identity%20would%20not%20have%20been%20so%20primary.%E2%80%9D%20But%20given%20the%20realities%20of%20today%2C%20she%20felt%20she%20had%20to%20%E2%80%9Cbe%20authentic%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChauhan%20spoke%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20about%20her%20book%2C%20censorship%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20India%20and%20more.%20Edited%20excerpts%20from%20the%20interview%20follow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThis%20is%20now%20your%20second%20murder%20mystery.%20What%20led%20to%20the%20change%20in%20genre%3F%20Is%20the%20writing%20process%20very%20different%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20more%20mathematical.%20Because%20in%20a%20romance%20you%20can%20pretty%20much%20start%20off%20and%20see%20where%20you%20go%2C%20but%20here%20the%20plotting%20needs%20to%20be%20more%20careful.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20need%20to%20know%20who%20did%20it.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20need%20to%20know%20who%20did%20it%2C%20and%20you%20need%20to%20leave%20enough%20clues%2C%20but%20you%20need%20to%20hide%20them%20also.%20And%20the%20timeline%E2%80%A6%20there%E2%80%99s%20that.%20So%20it%E2%80%99s%20more%20plotted%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20more%20scaffolding%20that%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20show%20once%20the%20skin%20is%20on%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20my%20reading%20of%20all%20your%20novels%2C%20across%20genres%2C%20there%20is%20an%20underlying%20subtle%2C%20humorous%20social%20commentary.%20It%E2%80%99s%20very%20much%20based%20in%20our%20present%2C%20both%20very%20locally%20and%20nationally.%20What%20drew%20you%20to%20that%20style%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20one%20of%20the%20main%20reasons%20I%20write.%20I%20love%20observing%20this%20stuff%2C%20and%20recording%20it%2C%20and%20laughing%20about%20it.%20I%E2%80%99m%20sometimes%20angry%2C%20but%20I%E2%80%99m%20mostly%20affectionate%2C%20I%20think.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20our%20current%20socio-political%20realities%2C%20where%20there%20are%20very%20present%20forms%20of%20censorship%2C%20like%20recently%20things%20being%20taken%20off%20Netflix%20for%20instance%2C%20affect%20writers%20like%20you%20who%20have%20a%20social%20commentary%20in%20their%20writing%2C%20even%20if%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20the%20main%20feature%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20just%20sad%2C%20I%20think.%20It%E2%80%99s%20depressing.%20You%20can%E2%80%99t%20get%20on%20to%20X%20%E2%80%93%20you%20see%20two%20posts%20about%20Gaza%2C%20or%20two%20posts%20about%20a%20movie%20like%20this%C2%A0%3Cem%3EAnnapoorani%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20the%20kind%20of%20hate%20people%20put.%20If%20you%20scroll%20through%20the%20comments%2C%20and%20you%20see%20that%20everyone%20clearly%20seems%20to%20think%20that%20this%20is%20the%20correct%20thing%20to%20do%2C%20and%20they%E2%80%99re%20so%20uninformed.%20When%20did%20we%20say%20that%20Kshatriyas%20don%E2%80%99t%20eat%20meat%2C%20for%20heaven%E2%80%99s%20sake.%20And%20what%20about%C2%A0%3Cem%3EBajrangi%20Bhaijaan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20it%20came%20out%20in%202016.%20So%20if%20you%20start%20going%20down%20that%20rabbit%20hole%20you%20really%20lose%20it%2C%20I%20think.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20think%20this%20is%20the%20time%20to%20go%20not%20ostrich-y%2C%20but%20somewhere%20hold%20on%20to%20your%20beliefs.%20Because%20otherwise%20the%20world%20will%20convince%20you%20that%20you%E2%80%99re%20the%20crazy%20one.%20It%E2%80%99s%20nuts.%20It%20just%20feels%20sad%2C%20that%20there%E2%80%99s%20an%20incomplete%20temple%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20being%20consecrated.%20I%20think%20it%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20disconnect.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20reached%20a%20point%20where%20I%E2%80%99ve%20stopped%20trying%20to%20convince%20people%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20exhausted.%20So%20I%E2%80%99ll%20save%20my%20energy%20and%20I%E2%80%99ll%20write%20about%20it%20gently%2C%20in%20my%20own%20way%2C%20and%20do%20what%20I%20can%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20much%20has%20this%20affected%20the%20literature%20and%20popular%20culture%20landscape%20in%20India%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%2C%20of%20course%20it%20has.%20People%20are%20pandering%20to%20the%20reigning%20mentality%20in%20all%20sorts%20of%20ways%2C%20some%20subtle%20ways%20and%20some%20not-so-subtle%20ways%2C%20and%20other%20people%20are%20being%20emboldened.%20In%20the%20dark%20places%20of%20your%20mind%2C%20if%20you%20want%20to%20slap%20your%20girlfriend%2C%20now%20you%E2%80%99ll%20think%20it%E2%80%99s%20fine%2C%20you%20can%20do%20it.%20We%E2%80%99re%20loosening%20the%20leash%20on%20monsters%20of%20all%20sorts%2C%20to%20crazy%20applause.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20also%20write%20regular%20columns%20in%20addition%20to%20your%20novels.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20I%20write%20for%20a%20good%20Malayali%20publication%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Week%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0magazine.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20been%20writing%20it%20for%20alm