nderwent%20surgery.%20Following%20the%20surgical%20procedure%2C%20we%20had%20to%20purchase%20a%20medical%20bed%20as%20he%20was%20on%20complete%20bed%20rest%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjayan%E2%80%99s%20father%20remained%20bedridden%20for%20several%20weeks%2C%20undergoing%20physiotherapy%20and%20various%20treatments.%20%E2%80%9CGradually%2C%20his%20condition%20improved%2C%20allowing%20him%20to%20transition%20to%20a%20wheelchair.%20After%20about%20a%20month%2C%20he%20progressed%20to%20using%20a%20walker%20and%20eventually%20a%20walking%20stick%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20he%20used%20the%20walking%20stick%20until%20the%20end%2C%20the%20other%20equipment%20became%20redundant.%20It%E2%80%99s%20impractical%20to%20keep%20a%20large%20bed%20at%20home%20when%20it%E2%80%99s%20no%20longer%20needed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjayan%20also%20realised%20that%20the%20cost%20of%20these%20items%20was%20quite%20expensive%20and%20might%20be%20unaffordable%20to%20many.%20%E2%80%9CI%20approached%20the%20sellers%20of%20these%20types%20of%20equipment%20and%20inquired%20whether%20they%20would%20take%20them%20back%20or%20if%20there%20was%20someone%20else%20in%20need.%20Surprisingly%2C%20they%20declined%2C%20suggesting%20I%20either%20give%20them%20to%20a%20scrap%20collector%20or%20to%20my%20local%20newspaper%20vendor%2C%20who%20could%20sell%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjayan%20did%20not%20want%20to%20sell%20the%20items%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F310812%2Fmukul-chhabra-scrapuncle-delhi-startup-collects-recycles-scrap-wins-lakhs-shark-tank%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Escrap%20collector%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20decided%20to%20think%20of%20some%20other%20way.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20my%20initial%20plan%20was%20to%20establish%20a%20website%20for%20people%20to%20donate%20and%20acquire%20items%20based%20on%20their%20needs%2C%20funding%2